(29, 'Hng dn thc hin nhim v nm hc 2011-2012 i vi gio dc tiu hc', 'hng-dn-thc-hin-nhim-v-nm-hc-2011-2012-i-vi-giao-dc-tiu-hc', '', '<p class="arialTitle">Hng dn thc hin nhim v nm hc 2011-2012 i vi gio dc tiu hc</p>\r\n<p style="background: none repeat scroll 0% 0% #efefef; padding-top: 5px; padding-left: 5px; padding-bottom: 5px;">\r\n<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr class="txtNhodi">\r\n<td>S t liu:</td>\r\n<td><b>5438/BGDT-GDTH</b></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="txtNhodi">\r\n<td>Ngy ban hnh:</td>\r\n<td><b>17-08-2011</b></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="txtNhodi">\r\n<td>Tp nh km:</td>\r\n<td><span style="color: #0000ff;"><b><a><span style="color: #0000ff;">5438GDTH.doc</span></a></b></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</p>\r\n<p align="center">Knh gi: Cc S Gio dc v o to</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Cn c Ch th s 3398/CT-BGDT ngy 12/8/2011 ca B trng B Gio dc v o to v nhim v trng tm cagio dc mm non, gio dc ph thng, gio dc thng xuyn v gio dc chuyn nghip nm hc 2011 - 2012;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Cn c Quyt nh s 2094/Q-BGDT ngy 20 thng 5 nm 2011 ca B trng B Gio dc v o to v vic ban hnh khung k hoch thi gian nm hc 2011 - 2012 ca gio dc mm non, gio dc ph thng v gio dc thng xuyn;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">B Gio dc v o to hng dn cc S Gio dc v o to thc hin nhim v nm hc 2011 - 2012 i vi cp Tiu hc nh sau:</p>\r\n<div align="center"><b>A - NHIM V CHUNG</b></div>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Nm hc 2011  2012 l nm hc u tin thc hin Ngh quyt i hi XI ca ng v i mi cn bn, ton din gio dc Vit Nam theo hng chun ha, hin i ha, x hi ha, dn ch ha v hi nhp quc t, gio dc tiu hc tp trung thc hin nhng nhim v trng tm sau:</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Tip tc thc hin cc cuc vn ng Hc tp v lm theo tm gng o c H Ch Minh, "Mi thy gio, c gio l mt tm gng o c, t hc v sng to" v phong tro thi ua "Xy dng trng hc thn thin, hc sinh tch cc".</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Tp trung ch o vic qun l, t chc dy hc theo chun kin thc, k nng; iu chnh ni dung dy hc v nh gi, xp loi ph hp c im tm l, sinh l hc sinh tiu hc; tng cng gio dc o c, gio dc k nng sng; i mi phng php dy hc; tng cng c hi tip cn gio dc cho tr em c hon cnh kh khn; tng cng ting Vit cho hc sinh dn tc thiu s; trin khai dy hc ngoi ng theo chng trnh mi  nhng ni c  iu kin; duy tr, cng c v nng cao cht lng ph cp gio dc tiu hc ng  tui; y mnh xy dng trng chun quc gia v t chc dy hc 2 bui/ngy.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">i mi mnh m cng tc qun l ch o, bi dng gio vin v cn b qun l gio dc;  cao trch nhim, khuyn khch s sng to ca gio vin v cn b qun l gio dc. y mnh vic ng dng cng ngh thng tin trong dy hc v qun l.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Ni dung chi tit trong tp nh km.</p>', '', 1, 23, 0, 113, '2011-11-19 14:07:41', 62, '', '2011-11-21 04:19:03', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-11-19 14:05:22', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '', 2, 0, 3, '', '', 0, 12, ''),
(30, 'Thng t ban hnh iu l trng tiu hc', 'thong-t-ban-hanh-iu-l-trng-tiu-hc', '', '<p style="background: none repeat scroll 0% 0% #efefef; padding-top: 5px; padding-left: 5px; padding-bottom: 5px;">\r\n<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr class="txtNhodi">\r\n<td>S t liu:</td>\r\n<td><b>41/2010/TT-BGDT</b></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="txtNhodi">\r\n<td>Ngy ban hnh:</td>\r\n<td><b>30-12-2010</b></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="txtNhodi">\r\n<td>Ngun:</td>\r\n<td><b>n v thuc B GD&T</b></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="txtNhodi">\r\n<td>Tp nh km:</td>\r\n<td><b><span style="color: #0000ff;"><a><span style="color: #0000ff;">41TT.rar</span></a></span></b></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Cn c Lut Gio dc ngy 14 thng 6 nm 2005; Lut sa i, b sung mt s iu ca Lut Gio dc ngy 25 thng 11 nm 2009;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Cn c Ngh nh s 178/2007/N-CP ngy 03 thng 12 nm 2007 ca Chnh ph quy nh chc nng, nhim v, quyn hn v c cu t chc ca b, c quan ngang b;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Cn c Ngh nh s 32/2008/N-CP ngy 19 thng 3 nm 2008 ca Chnh ph quy nh chc nng, nhim v, quyn hn v c cu t chc ca B Gio dc v o to;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Cn c Ngh nh s 75/2006/N-CP ngy 02 thng 8 nm 2006 ca Chnh ph quy nh chi tit v hng dn thi hnh mt s iu ca Lut Gio dc;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Cn c Ngh nh s 115/2010/N-CP ngy 24 thng 12 nm 2010 ca Chnh ph quy nh trch nhim qun l nh nc v gio dc;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Theo  ngh ca V trng V Gio dc Tiu hc,</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">B trng B Gio dc v o to quyt nh:</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><b>iu 1.</b> Ban hnh km theo Thng t ny iu l Trng tiu hc.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><b>iu 2.</b> Thng t ny c hiu lc thi hnh t ngy 15 thng 02 nm 2011. Thng t ny thay th Quyt nh s 51/2007/Q-BGDT ngy 31 thng 8 nm 2007 ca B trng B Gio dc v o to ban hnh iu l Trng tiu hc. Cc quy nh trc y tri vi quy nh ti Thng t ny u b bi b.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><b>iu 3.</b> Chnh Vn phng, V trng V Gio dc Tiu hc, th trng cc n v c lin quan thuc B Gio dc v o to, Ch tch U ban nhn dn cc tnh, thnh ph trc thuc trung ng, Gim c s gio dc v o to chu trch nhim thi hnh Thng t ny.</p>\r\n<table style="width: 100%;" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top" width="349">\r\n<div><span style="font-size: xx-small;"><b><i>Ni nhn:</i></b></span></div>\r\n<span style="font-size: xx-small;">\r\n<div><span style="font-size: xx-small;">- Ban Tuyn gio Trung ng;</span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-size: xx-small;">- Vn phng Quc hi;</span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-size: xx-small;">- Vn phng Chnh ph;</span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-size: xx-small;">- UBVHGDTNTN&N ca Quc hi;</span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-size: xx-small;">- Hi ng quc gia gio dc;</span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-size: xx-small;">- Cc b, c quan ngang b, c quan thuc Chnh ph;</span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-size: xx-small;">- UBND cc tnh, thnh ph trc thuc T;</span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-size: xx-small;">- Nh iu 3 ( thc hin);</span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-size: xx-small;">- Cc kim tra vn bn QPPL (B T php);</span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-size: xx-small;">- Cng bo;</span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-size: xx-small;">- Kim ton nh nc;</span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-size: xx-small;">- Website Chnh ph;</span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-size: xx-small;">- Website B GD&T;</span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-size: xx-small;">- Lu VT, V PC, V GDTH.</span></div>\r\n</span></td>\r\n<td valign="top" width="273">\r\n<div align="center"><span style="font-size: xx-small;"><b>KT. B TRNG</b></span></div>\r\n<div align="center"><span style="font-size: xx-small;"><b>TH TRNG</b></span></div>\r\n<div align="center"><b></b><span style="font-size: xx-small;"><b> k</b></span></div>\r\n<div align="center"><b></b></div>\r\n<div align="center"></div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', '', 1, 23, 0, 113, '2011-11-19 14:09:44', 62, '', '2011-11-21 04:16:20', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-11-19 14:09:15', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '', 2, 0, 2, '', '', 0, 20, ''),
(31, 'Thng t ban hnh quy nh nh gi v xp loi hc sinh tiu hc', 'thong-t-ban-hanh-quy-nh-anh-gia-va-xp-loi-hc-sinh-tiu-hc', '', '<p style="background: none repeat scroll 0% 0% #efefef; padding-top: 5px; padding-left: 5px; padding-bottom: 5px;">\r\n<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr class="txtNhodi">\r\n<td>S t liu:</td>\r\n<td><b>32/2009/TT-BGDT</b></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="txtNhodi">\r\n<td>Ngy ban hnh:</td>\r\n<td><b>27-10-2009</b></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="txtNhodi">\r\n<td>Ngun:</td>\r\n<td><b>n v thuc B GD&T</b></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="txtNhodi">\r\n<td>Tp nh km:</td>\r\n<td><span style="color: #0000ff;"><b><a><span style="color: #0000ff;">32-2009-TT-BGDDT.pdf</span></a></b></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</p>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;">Cn c Lut Gio dc ngy 14 thng 6 nm 2005;</div>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Cn c Ngh nh s 178/2007/N-CP ngy 03 thng 12 nm 2007 ca Chnh ph quy nh chc nng, nhim v, quyn hn v c cu t chc ca B, c quan ngang B;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Cn c Nghnh s 32/2008/N-CP ngy 19 thng 3 nm 2008 ca Chnh ph quy nh chc nng, nhim v, quyn hn v c cu t chc ca B Gio dc v o to;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Cn c Nghnh s 75/2006/N-CP ngy 02 thng 8 nm 2006 ca Chnh ph quy nh chi tit v hng dn thi hnh mt s iu ca Lut Gio dc;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Cn c Ch th s 14/2001/CT-TTg ngy 11 thng 6 nm 2001 ca Th tng Chnh ph v vici mi chng trnh gio dc ph thng thc hin Ngh quyt s 40/2000/QH10 ca Quc hi;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Cn c Quytnh s 16/2006/Q-BGDT ngy 05 thng 5 nm 2006 ca B trng B Gio dc v o to v vic ban hnh Chng trnh gio dc ph thng;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Cn c Quytnh s 51/2007/Q-BGDT ngy 31 thng 8 nm 2007 ca B trng B Gio dc v o to v vic ban hnh iu l trng tiu hc;</p>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;">Theo  ngh ca V trng V Gio dc Tiu hc,</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;">B trng B Gio dc v o to Quyt nh:</div>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><b>iu 1</b>. Ban hnh km theo Thng t ny Quy nh v nh gi v xp loi hc sinh tiu hc.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><b>iu 2</b>.Thng t ny c hiu lc thi hnh t ngy 11 thng 12 nm 2009.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Thng t ny thay th Quyt nh s 30/2005/Q-BGDT ngy 30 thng 9 nm 2005 ca B trng B Gio dc v o to ban hnh Quy nh nh gi v xp loi hc sinh tiu hc. Cc quy nh trc y tri vi quy nh ti Thng t ny u b bi b.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><b>iu 3</b>. Chnh Vn phng, V trng V Gio dc Tiu hc, Cc trng</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Cc Kho th v Kim nh cht lng gio dc, Th trng cc n v c lin quan thuc B Gio dc v o to, Gim c cc s gio dc v o to chu trch nhim thi hnh Thng t ny.</p>\r\n<table style="width: 100%;" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top" width="295">\r\n<div><span style="font-size: xx-small;"><b>Ni nhn: </b></span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-size: xx-small;">- Vn phng Quc hi;</span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-size: xx-small;">- Vn phng Chnh ph;<br /> - Hi ng Quc gia gio dc;<br /> - Ban Tuyn gio Trung ng; </span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-size: xx-small;">- Kim ton nh nc;<br /> - Cc KTVBQPPL (B T php); </span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-size: xx-small;">- Nh iu 3;</span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-size: xx-small;">- Cng bo;</span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-size: xx-small;">- Website Chnh ph;</span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-size: xx-small;">- Website B GD&T;</span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-size: xx-small;">- Lu: VT, V PC, V GDTH.</span></div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign="top" width="295">\r\n<div align="center"><span style="font-size: xx-small;"><b>KT. B TRNG</b></span></div>\r\n<div align="center"><span style="font-size: xx-small;"><b>TH TRNG</b></span></div>\r\n<div align="center"><b></b></div>\r\n<div align="center"><span style="font-size: xx-small;"><b>Nguyn Vinh Hin</b></span></div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', '', 1, 23, 0, 113, '2011-11-19 14:10:47', 62, '', '2011-11-24 13:36:58', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-11-19 14:10:24', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '', 3, 0, 1, '', '', 0, 36, ''),
(33, 'Th im dy hc bng phim cho hc sinh tiu hc', 'thi-im-dy-hc-bng-phim-cho-hc-sinh-tiu-hc', '', '<p style="text-align: left;"></p>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;" class="fon33 mt1">Bin nhng bi hc kh khan thnh nhng hnh nh trc quan, thc t v sinh ng l mc tiu ca d n Skycare - Khoa hc sng ng trong mt em do Tp on Gio dc UNET thc hin.</div>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Theo , mi tp phim s chuyn ti trn vn ni dung ca mt bi ging trn lp ca hc sinh tiu hc, v d nh hnh nh mt ht cy ny mm c quay chm t khi m chi n tch l mm thnh cy con. Ngoi ra, trong phim cn c nhn vt anh Tri t ng nghnh v c dn bi hai hc sinh tiu hc.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">i din tp on ny cho bit, nhng dn chng thc t sinh ng bng hnh nh, on phim chn thc s gip cc em nh tip thu bi ging d dng v hng th hn,</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">nh gi cao v  tng nhng trong bui Tp on Gio dc UNET ra mt sn phm ny, nhiu gio vin tiu hc ca <a href="http://vatgia.com/home/quicksearch.php?keyword=H%C3%A0+N%E1%BB%99i" target="_blank"><b>H Ni</b></a> khng khi bn khon khi khng c xem trn vn <a href="http://vatgia.com/1033/bat-dia.html" target="_blank"><b>a</b></a> phim do pha Tp on ny cha cng b.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">ng Phm Xun Tin, Trng phng Gio dc Tiu hc, S GD-T H Ni cho rng, khi cha xem a phim, gio vin cng kh hnh dung s kt hp dy nh th no. Bn cnh , trc khi c ng dng rng ri, sn phm ny cn c kim nh v dy th im.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">y cng l  kin ca ng Nguyn Hu Hnh, Ph v trng V Gio dc Tiu hc, B GD-T. ng Hnh nhn mnh rng, vic cc <a href="http://www.finalstyle.com/Doanh-Nghiep-Nen-Xem/" target="_blank"><b>doanh nghip</b></a> u t cho thit b gio dc l rt ng qu v B hon ton ng h. Tuy nhin, trc khi a vo ng dng thc tin, cc thit b ny cn c m bo v cht lng.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">i din ca Tp on Gio dc UNET cho bit, n v ny d kin s dy th im  H Ni trong thng ny.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;" align="right"><strong>Theo <span style="font-style: italic;">Vietnam+</span></strong></p>', '', 1, 24, 0, 118, '2011-11-19 14:13:25', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-11-19 14:11:41', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '', 1, 0, 5, '', '', 0, 27, ''),
(34, '18 tnh th im chng trnh ting Anh tiu hc', '18-tnh-thi-im-chng-trinh-ting-anh-tiu-hc', '', '<p></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"><em>\r\n<p>\r\n<table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 1px;" align="left" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 1px;" align="left" border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img alt="18 tnh th im chng trnh ting Anh tiu hc " src="http://image.tin247.com/vnmedia/100909010544-15-373.jpg" border="0" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"><em><strong></strong> - B GD&T cho bit, nm hc 2010  2011, s c 18 tnh, thnh ph vi 88 lp bt u trin khai th im chng trnh ting Anh tiu hc.</em></span></p>\r\n</em> <br /></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Tu theo nng lc ca cc trng, mi tnh, thnh c khong 2 n 9 trng  iu kin tham gia chng trnh. Trong  H Ni c 9 trng; Hi Phng 6 trng; Nam nh 5 trng; Vnh Phc 5 trng; Hi Dng 4 trng; Thi Bnh 4 trng; Thanh Ha 6 trng; Ngh An 8 trng; Tha Thin - Hu 3 trng;  Nng 4 trng; Khnh Ha 3 trng; thnh ph H Ch Minh9 trng; ng Nai: 4; B Ra- Vng Tu: 4; Cn Th: 5; H Nam: 2; H Tnh: 4; Ho Bnh: 3 trng. </span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Theo  n ca B GD&T, d kin t nm hc 2010-2011 s trin khai dy ngoi ng theo chng trnh mi cho khong 20% lng hc sinh lp 3 v m rng dn quy m  t khong 70% vo nm hc 2015-2016 v 100% vo nm 2018-2019.</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Trc , B GD&T quy nh cc trng tiu hc c chn th im chng trnh Ting Anh tiu hc mi s dy vi thi lng 4 tit/tun. Cc trng khc ch ng, linh hot trong vic la chn ni dung, chng trnh, ti liu dy hc trn c s ph hp iu kin thc t v nhu cu chnh ng ca hc sinh theo hai phng n. Phng n 1: Thc hin dy hc ngoi ng t chn t lp 3, thi lng 2 tit/ tun, hoc nhiu hn 2 tit/ tun. Phng n 2: Khuyn khch trin khai cc chng trnh ting Anh tng cng v lm quen ting Anh bt u t lp 1  nhng ni c iu kin v c nhu cu ca hc sinh.</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Lu nay, vic dy v hc ting Anh trong nh trng vn khng my hiu qu v phng php c, cng nhc, ch yu l hc ng php v t mi, nu yu cu ca  n mi c p ng, cc gio vin phi c tp hun k cng  thay i phng php dy hc. Hin ti, phng php ch o trong vic dy ting Anh tiu hc m B GD&T a ra l dy ngn ng giao tip, hot ng dy hc c t chc thng qua mi trng giao tip a dng, phong ph vi cc hot ng tng tc (tr chi, bi ht, k chuyn, cu , v tranh...), di cc hnh thc hot ng c nhn, theo cp v nhm. Theo phng php ny, hc sinh c luyn tp kt hp cc k nng nghe, ni, c, vit, gio vin to c hi ti a cho hc sinh s dng ting Anh trong lp hc</span></p>', '', 1, 24, 0, 118, '2011-11-19 14:15:14', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-11-19 14:14:04', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '', 1, 0, 4, '', '', 0, 40, '');
