(35, 'Cch ngi M dy hc sinh tiu hc', 'cach-ngi-m-dy-hc-sinh-tiu-hc', '', '<p style="color: black;" class="text" align="justify"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 8pt;" size="2" face="Arial">ng lc ng sau mt cng quc kinh t l g? Rt cc h  c mt nn gio dc nh th no? Sau y l bi vit ca mt tc gi ngi Trung Quc v nn gio dc tiu hc M cng vi cc cu chuyn  bn c tin so snh hai nn gio dc M  Trung Quc.</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" size="2" face="Arial"><strong>Mc tiu gio dc tiu hc M</strong></span></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" size="2" face="Arial">Cho d l ngi Hoa  M, bn cng kh hiu r c u l trnh  tri thc m hc sinh tiu hc  M phi t n, sau y ch l mt tiu chun s lc  tham kho.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" size="2" face="Arial"><em>1. Tt nghip mu gio</em></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" size="2" face="Arial">C th nhn bit v phn bit con s, c th biu t khi nim ton hc tru tng bng nhng vt th c th nh hn si, mu giy, ci que; nhn bit 26 ch ci ting Anh, phn bit nguyn m v ph m; phn bit c cc ngnh ngh khc nhau i  lm nhng g, v d nh bc s, gio vin, ngi a th, cnh st, cnh st phng chy cha chy hiu c qu trnh din bin ca cuc i sinh vt, bao gm sinh, lo, bnh, t ca con ngi, su bin thnh bm,; hc a l t a cu, bn ; hiu c rng trn tri t c rt nhiu c dn, rt nhiu quc gia v nhng mu da khc nhau, hiu c rng ngi cn  trong nh, tr em cn n trng, ngi trng thnh cn i lm</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" size="2" face="Arial"><em>2. Lp 1</em></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" size="2" face="Arial">C th m t 1 n 100, c th m s c hai ch s hoc th no l bi s ca 5, bit s l v s chn, bit php cng tr n gin; hc cch quan st, chia ngnh phn loi i vi nhng s vt v vt phm khc nhau; c th ly dn chng v qu trnh din bin ca s sng, hiu c quan h sng tng tr gia ng thc vt trong thin nhin; hc s dng tranh nh  biu t ; hiu tnh tt yu ca vic mc, n,  v mi m gia nh; hiu r quan h gia cc thnh vin trong gia nh, gia nhng ngi lng xm.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" size="2" face="Arial"><em>3. Lp 2</em></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" size="2" face="Arial">Bit c, vit s c ba ch s, t nm s ty  chn, c th m xui hoc m ngc; vn dng thnh tho php cng tr i vi s c hai ch s, bit dng nhng n v o lng nh inch (tc Anh) hoc centimet  o  di, bit xem ng h; c sch, duy tr u n vic vit (nhn xt, bnh lun) sau khi c sch, hc cch vit tng kt, hiu v phn bit c nhng hnh thc vn hc khc nhau nh: th, tn vn, tiu thuyt, truyn k, bit c s khc nhau gia tc phm h cu v tc phm phi h cu; bt u hc nghin cu c lp v ng vt, v d nh vn  sinh thi ca cn trng</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" size="2" face="Arial"><em>4. Lp 3</em></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" size="2" face="Arial">Hc c cch bin t liu thnh biu ; bit so snh s ln nh v cng tr trong phm vi 100.000, thnh tho php cng, tr, nhn, chia i vi s c ba ch s; c th ly nhng ti liu ti ch trong mi trng xung quanh, su tp, t chc ti liu, hiu c cch gi gn sc khe ca con ngi, hiu r qu trnh din bin cuc i ca nhng ng vt nh nh: ch, bm, g con, chut bch; hiu cch s dng t in; c th hiu t tng ca nhng tc phm v cc nh vn, ha s mnh yu thch biu t, hiu c cc tc phm vn hc trong cc bi cnh vn ha khc nhau.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" size="2" face="Arial"><em>5. Lp 4</em></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" size="2" face="Arial">Dng my tnh  tnh ton nhng con s rt ln, so snh ln nh trong phm vi 1.000.000, hc s thp phn v phn s, v biu ; c th gii thch s khc nhau ca kh hu gia cc vng t trn th gii nh bn , hnh nh, biu ; thng qua vic c, hiu thm mt bc v nhng th loi vn hc khc nhau, v d nh tc phm khoa hc vin tng, truyn k,</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" size="2" face="Arial"><em>6. Lp 5</em></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" size="2" face="Arial">Bit in, c cc loi bng biu, thnh tho cc php tnh cng, tr, nhn, chia phn s; c th vn dng h thng th vin v cc t liu  tin hnh nghin cu; tin hnh so snh v tng hp cc loi tin tc thng qua vic vit bt k; bt u t vit nhng bi vn dng t tht (phi h cu) v nhng on vn theo th thc nm on; hc c cch vit chnh thc, khng chnh thc v cch vit th cho bn b; hiu vic chia ngnh phn loi nhng sch bo khc nhau, c th nm c ni dung ch yu ca mt cun sch, ng thi tin hnh bnh lun v cu t, bi cnh, cch xy dng nhn vt, phng thc biu t, ngh thut ngn ng.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" size="2" face="Arial">Gi tr c bn ca vn ha M<br /> </span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" size="2" face="Arial">C l nhiu ngi trong chng ta s c cm gic rng, mt hc sinh hc lp 5, chun b tt nghip tiu hc m yu cu v nng lc ton hc ch l bit cng, tr, nhn, chia, th trnh  thp qu.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" size="2" face="Arial">Mt c gio mu gio v hu thy hc sinh tiu hc M sut ngy ch bit chi th khng khi ngc nhin v lo lng cho cu chu Hoa kiu  M ca mnh. B ni vi m ca cu b: Nu l  Trung Quc, p lc ca hc sinh chun b tt nghip tiu hc rt ln, c ngy phi cm u vo lm bi tp Nhng chu ti th sao? Mi ngy tan hc v l i  bng, chi bng bu dc cng l tr thi gian cho vic lm bi, tp n t nh th, lm m th phi ch !</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" size="2" face="Arial">Ngi m ni, thnh tch ca chu  trng hu nh l im A, tr i khi ngu nhin sai st, nhiu ln chu em v ton im 100. i vi hc sinh tiu hc  M th nh vy l  ri. Gio dc tiu hc khng phi l gio dc tinh anh, cn to iu kin pht trin ton din cho tr, ch trng vic kt bn, vn ng v nhng hot ng ngoi kha.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" size="2" face="Arial">ng nhin, ngi b ca cu b vn khng bng lng, b ni bi ging ca M qu nh nhng, bi tp qu n gin, th chc thi c cng rt d dng. B nhn mnh, ngi Trung Quc chng ti coi trng cc nn tng c s vng chc. K thc, ngi M cng coi trng vic xy dng nn tng.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" size="2" face="Arial">Ch c iu ci gi l c s ca ngi Trung Quc v ngi M khc nhau. Ngi M coi trng nn tng lm ngi, quan nim ny  c bi p t nh. C s m hc sinh  M cn to dng l  thc t tin, thnh thc, lng thin, cng bng, bao dung v c lp t ch  lm ngi, cng c ngha l, ngay t nh, h  hc c gi tr c bn ca vn ha M, ch khng phi l tri thc  phc v gi tr c bn ny.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" size="2" face="Arial">Tuy nhin, cng phi ni thm l c rt nhiu ngi Trung Quc suy ngh nh ngi b k trn, coi gio dc trung tiu hc  M l hng bt, m nhiu nht trong s  khng ai khc chnh l nhng gio vin trung tiu hc  Trung Quc. Ci m h c  l nhng hc sinh ng u trong danh sch ot gii thng ton quc t hng nm lun l nhng hc sinh Trung Quc, gio dc trung tiu hc  M khng th so snh c vi Trung Quc. C ln, trn mt t bo Trung vn  M cn c mt bi vit mang tn: So v ton hc, M ch c th c coi l nc ang pht trin.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" size="2" face="Arial">Trong mt cuc hp ca ngi Hoa, cc bc cha m nh li nhng cu chuyn thi tr ca mnh, mt n s  thng thn ni, tiu chun chn chng khi  dng nh u phi l hc gii, cng c ngha l thnh tch tt, ngoi hnh, tnh tnh, tu dng u l th yu. Trong mt ca cc n sinh ch c nhng ngi ng u lp mi l tt, ngi ng u ton nm li cng tt.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" size="2" face="Arial">Nhng gi y, th h sau ca chng ta th sao? Nu nh bn hi ai l bn nam c thnh tch hc tp tt nht trong lp th con gi bn t tr nn lng tng, nhng nu hi, bn nam no gii th thao nht trng, th con bn s r nh lng bn tay vy. Nu bn tng bc mt c gi xinh p no , bo rng c s ly c mt trng nguyn, th c gi s cho rng khng xng ng, thm ch cn cm thy thua thit, Ci g, ai thm ci  mt sch ?.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" size="2" face="Arial">Nhng ngi hc gii nht (nu ch bit hc tp, khng c s thch, s trng no khc) thng b bn b c lp.  trnh mt i tnh bn,  c bit n nhiu hn, c hoan nghnh nhiu hn, khng t hc sinh xut sc  t chi hc cc lp cht lng cao (lp vinh d), s mt i nhng ngi bn c t lp ph thng, thm ch c mt s hc sinh cn c tnh lm bi sai trong k thi  ha ng vi bn b. Trong mt ca bn tr, bn b, tnh bn, nim vui quan trng hn thnh tch rt nhiu.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" size="2" face="Arial"> kh trong bi tp ca hc sinh tiu hc M</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" size="2" face="Arial">Mt ngi cha Trung Quc a cu con trai chn tui ti M, cho con vo hc mt ngi trng  M th trong lng lo lng v cng, khng hiu  l trng hc kiu g! Trong lp hc sinh t do ty  tho lun, c th ci m ; gio vin v hc sinh thng xuyn cng ngi bt trn mt t khng phn bit ln b; vo gi hc m c nh ang chi tr chi; Ba gi chiu  l tan hc; li khng c sch gio khoa thng nht.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" size="2" face="Arial">ng em cho gio vin xem bi hc tiu hc lp 4 m con ng  hc  Trung Quc, gio vin ni vi ng, cho ti lp 6, con trai ng khng phi hc thm mn ton na. Lc , ng bt u hi hn v em con n M m lm l vic hc ca con.  Trung Quc, cp sch ca hc sinh nng trch nhng tri thc, cn nhn con mnh by gi, mi ngy mang ci cp nh tnh n trng, i hc nh i chi. Mt hc k nhy mt  ht, ng khng khi ngh ngi, hi con, n tng su sc nht khi n M hc l g? Cu b p: T do.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" size="2" face="Arial">Li mt bn, c tan hc, a tr li chy ti th vin ri mang mt l sch v nh, th m cha ti hai ngy  tr. ng li hi, mn sch nhiu nh th  lm g? Con trai p: Lm bi tp. Sau , ng nhn thy tn bi tp m cu b ang lm trn my vi tnh Hm qua v hm nay ca Trung Quc, ng kinh ngc sut ng, y l ch  mn hc g vy? Th hi v no ang lm tin s dm m  ti ln nh th?</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" size="2" face="Arial">ng cht vn con trai, y l ch  ca ai, cu b hn nhin p: Thy gio ni, M l mt nc di dn, mi hc sinh u cn vit mt bi v t nc m t tin mnh  sinh sng, cn phi phn tch s khc bit so vi nc M da trn a l, lch s, nhn vn, ng thi phi a ra quan im v cch nhn ca mnh. Ngi cha im lng.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" size="2" face="Arial">My ngy sau, ng thy bi tp ca con trai  xong, mt tp gm hn 20 trang giy, t Hong H chn khc n vn t tng hnh; t con ng t la ti l c ng tinh C bi vn c vit vi mt kh th ho hng, c l l, c cn c, phn chng phn tit, c bit l mt danh sch th mc tham kho  phn cui khin ngi cha khng khi bng hong, ci cch thc ca mt lun vn tin s ny, ngoi ba mi tui ng mi hc c.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" size="2" face="Arial">n khi sp kt thc hc k lp 6 ca con, ng li c mt phen cng li, gio vin a ra mt lot cu hi lin quan n Chin tranh th gii th hai, nghe nh mt k hun luyn trc khi ng c ca mt thng ngh s tng lai:</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" size="2" face="Arial">Bn cho rng ai nn chu trch nhim i vi cuc chin tranh ny?<br /> Theo bn, nguyn nhn tht bi ca ng Nazi (c) l g?</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" size="2" face="Arial">Nu bn l c vn cao cp ca tng thng Truman<sup>1</sup>, bn s t thi  g i vi vic M nm bom nguyn t?<br /> Bn c cho rng, bin php tt nht  kt thc chin tranh khi  ch l nm bom nguyn t?<br /> Theo bn, cch tt nht  trnh chin tranh ngy nay l g?<br /> Lch s nc M mi ch c vn vn 200 nm, nhng   sc m cnh ca tr tu ca cc em hc sinh.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" size="2" face="Arial">S khc bit gia cng nhn v ng ch</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" size="2" face="Arial">Ngi cha ny vn nh rng khi con trai ng tt nghip tiu hc, cu b  c th s dng thnh tho h thng my vi tnh v vi phim ca th vin  tra cu t liu v hnh nh. C ln, hai b con tranh lun v tp tnh sn mi ca s t v bo, ngy hm sau, cu con trai mn t th vin tp phim v ng vt ca Hi a l quc gia Hoa K, hai cha con va xem va tho lun. Hc sinh tiu hc ca M lc ny  hc c phng php tm p n  u mi khi c nghi vn. Ngoi th vin, hc sinh trung tiu hc  M cng tm ti liu trn cc trang web lin quan khi lm bi tp v mt s bo co nghin cu.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" size="2" face="Arial">Lu hc sinh Trung Quc ti M lm tin s, t lc vo hc ti lc tt nghip, ginh c hc v tin s cn nm nm. Trong vin nghin cu sinh, rt nhiu ngi c cm gic rng ngi M thng khng phi l i th ca lu hc sinh Trung Quc trong chuyn thi ly hc bng, nhng c ng ti lnh vc thc tin, lm mt vi vn  c tnh nghin cu, th ngi Trung Quc khng th linh hot c bng ngi M, khng c tnh sng to di do nh h.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" size="2" face="Arial">Ti khi cm c bng tin s  i tm vic, vit s yu l lch, h li lc hu mt bc ln, khng bit t qung b cho bn thn mnh. Khng th vit v bn thn mnh khng phi v h khng bit, m l v khng c  bn lnh  th hin ci ti ca mnh.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" size="2" face="Arial">ng nhin, iu ny c lin quan ti s bt ng gia gio dc v ton b h thng gio dc c s. Ngi Trung Quc ch quen pht huy bn lnh trong mt khung quy nh no , mt khi khng cn quy nh, mt i s ch o, khng nhn thy h thng quy chiu vn c na, th vi ngi M l ginh c t do, cn vi ngi Trung Quc, c l ch cn li cm gic mt phng hng, khng hong, trng rng, khng bit da vo u.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" size="2" face="Arial">Khi  cng tc c nm nm, mi nm, thc t y li cng r rng hn. Ngi Trung Quc thng ch c th lm k thut, cng lm l ln qun l mt b phn k thut no , dng nh khng my ai lm c gim c cng ty ln. Ngi Trung Quc khng phc nhng ng ch khng gii v k thut v thng bn khon: bn lnh ca h rt cc nm  u?</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" size="2" face="Arial">Bn lnh  l: hiu c s trng ca tng thnh vin trong cng ty, gip h pht huy tn lc s trng ca mnh, nhn vin v cng ty cng hp tc, nng cao gi tr ca cng ty mnh trong mt nh u t v khch hng, khng ngng thu ht thm vn u t v tng thm u ra cho sn phm Hin nhin, y l tc phm ca mt ng ch, ch khng phi ca mt cng nhn.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;" align="left"><strong><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" size="2" face="Arial"><em>Anh Sa (Dch t Vn co bo)</em></span></strong></p>', '', 1, 24, 0, 118, '2011-11-19 14:20:11', 62, '', '2011-11-25 06:58:13', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-11-21 14:19:00', '0000-0