(36, 'Dy tr cch s dng ng tin hiu qu', 'dy-tr-cach-s-dng-ng-tin-hiu-qu', '', '<h2 style="text-align: justify;" class="Lead"><span style="font-size: 8pt; color: #000000;">Khong 150 em hc sinh t lp 3 n lp 5 ti TP HCM s c Ngn hng HSBC Vit Nam dy v nhng k nng ti chnh c bn nh chi tiu, qun l tin bc sao cho ng tin c s dng hiu qu nht.</span></h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="Normal">&nbsp;Chng trnh gm 6 tit hc (mi tit mt gi ng h vo th by hng tun), din ra t ngy 15/10 n 19/11 ti 3 trng tiu hc Trn Hng o, qun 1, Trn Bnh Trng, qun 5 v Lng nh Ca, qun 3.</p>\r\n<p><img style="float: right;" src="http://vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3b/a3/0c/49/hsbc1b.jpg" height="146" width="196" border="1" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="Normal">Ni dung cc kha hc gm: tin trong ngn hng, nhn thc v gi tr, khm ph k nng, khi nghip, k nng ra quyt nh v thc hnh o c kinh doanh. Trong , tit u tin cc em c hc v cch qun l mt ti khon ngn hng, thng qua cc hnh nh gn gi nht vi cc em l con heo t. Sau , tit hc th hai s hng dn cc em xc nh ngnh ngh  khi nghip kinh doanh m tr c th lm  kim thu nhp.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="Normal">Tit hc th ba, hc sinh xc nh cc k nng, s thch c nhn v lin kt chng vi nhng c hi kinh doanh c th thc hin c. Bc tip theo l gip tng tr tm hiu nhng cn bn  bt u hot ng kinh doanh nh. Sau  dy v k nng ra quyt nh. Hc sinh s lm vic nhm vi nhau  tip tc thc hnh tit kim v chi tiu; cc phng php a ra quyt nh tiu dng thng minh.</p>\r\n', '\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="Normal">Cui cng l bui hc dy v o c kinh doanh. Cc em c hc cch nhn bit nhng thng tin qung co sai s tht v tm quan trng ca vic thc hnh o c kinh doanh.<img style="float: left;" src="http://vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3b/a3/0c/49/hsbc4b.jpg" height="152" width="201" border="1" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="Normal">B Bo Nhi, lp 4/4 trng tiu hc Trn Hng o, qun 1, cho bit, sau 3 bui hc u tin v k nng, b  hiu hn th no l tit kim. Chng hn nh b s khng i b m mua nhng  chi t tin, khng dng tin b m cho hng ngy  n vt m s b vo heo t. Cui thng hoc khi no cn mua nhng dng c hc tp b s p "ngn hng" ca mnh ra dng.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="Normal">Trong khi , b Quc Trm, hc sinh lp 4/7 th cho rng, gi b  hiu hn v tin ch ca vic gi tin tit kim vo ngn hng. C b cho bit, t nay mi ngy b s t b tin vo con heo t hoc mt chic v. Sau , b ghi chp vo cun s nh s tin b vo hoc ly ra hng ngy l bao nhiu?. "Cui nm, con s tng kt li, nu nhiu tin th nh m em gi ngn hng. V gi ngn hng th c tin li, cn  nh th khng", b Trm hn nhin ni.</p>\r\n<table style="width: 1px;" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="http://vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3b/a3/0c/49/hsbc3b.jpg" height="427" width="569" border="1" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="text-align: center;" class="Image">Thy v tr hc rt say sa. nh: <em>L Chi</em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="Normal">ng Sumit Dutta, Tng gim c Ngn hng HSBC Vit Nam hy vng, chng trnh s trang b cho hc sinh tiu hc nhng hiu bit c bn v ti chnh. Qua , khuyn khch cc em vn dng nhng k nng c hc vo thc tin hng ngy, gip mi b nhn thc c tm quan trng ca vic qun l ng tin.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="Normal">"Chng ti hy vng s gieo cho cc em nhng ht mm kin thc v kim tin v iu hnh kinh doanh  lm giu trong khun kh o c kinh doanh v cch s dng ng tin mt cch thng minh, hiu qu thng qua chi tiu cng nh u t", ng Sumit ni.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="Normal">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><strong>Theo vnexpress</strong></p>', 1, 25, 0, 135, '2011-11-19 14:23:51', 62, '', '2011-12-06 06:36:09', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-11-19 14:21:29', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nre