(37, '''Cng'' cp nng qu s nh hng n ct sng', 'cong-cp-nng-qua-s-nh-hng-n-ct-sng', '', '<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Nhng ngi lm gio dc cho rng nh trng v gia nh cn phi hp gip hc sinh c cp sch nh hn. Bi theo khuyn co ca chuyn gia y t, vic mang cp nng lu ngy s nh hng n chiu cao v ct sng.</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Trao i vi <em>VnExpress</em>, bc s phu thut ct sng Nguyn Hong Long (Bnh vin Vit c) cho bit, hin ti Vit Nam cha c nghin cu no v nh hng ca vic mang vc cp nng n s pht trin ca tr. Tuy nhin, nu vic ny ko di s nh hng khng nh n chiu cao v ct sng ca cc em.</span></p>\r\n<div style="overflow: hidden; text-align: justify;">\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="Normal">"Theo cc nghin cu th tnh trng vo ct sng tr em hc ng chim tng i cao, 10-35%. Mc  vo tin trin theo  tui t lp 1 n lp 9", bc s Long cung cp. Cch y hn mt nm, mt hc sinh  TP HCM  b gy xng n tri, ct sng b vo, g nh do eo cp nng i b mi ngy v ko di.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="Normal">Tha nhn vic hc sinh phi eo cp sch nng l rt ph bin  cc trng bn tr, c Cao Th Hng, Hiu trng trng tiu hc Mai Dch (Cu Giy, H Ni) cho rng nguyn nhn l ban gim hiu cha c gii php hp l v vic mang sch v cho hc sinh v ph huynh mua qu nhiu sch tham kho cho con.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="Normal">Nguyn V trng gio dc Tiu hc Nguyn K Ho ch ra nguyn nhn su xa l hc sinh phi hc qu nhiu. Hc  trng, v nh phi hc buc cc em phi mang sch v i, v. Ngoi ra, lut xut bn cng khng cm vic in sch v ti liu nn hng lot sch tham kho c in n, pht hnh. C sch th b m, thy c bt mua ri bt tr hc.</p>\r\n<table style="width: 1px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="text-align: justify;"><img src="http://vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3b/a2/ef/85/cap.jpg" height="350" width="480" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="Image">Nh trng cn c gii php gip hc sinh khng phi mang sch v nh nh c t cho hc sinh  , khng giao bi tp v nh.<em class="Image"></em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p class="Normal">PGS Vn Nh Cng so snh sch Ty nng hn sch ta nhiu ln v ba sch ca Ty cng, dy nn nu hc sinh Vit Nam phi mang sch Ty th cn nng hn hin nay. Tuy nhin, hc sinh Ty li khng phi mang sch v nh bi cc chu nh ch phi hc trn lp, v nh c ngh ngi th gin. Cn hc sinh ta th phi tn dng mi thi gian  hc, khng hc th b b m, thy c bt phi hc.</p>\r\n<p class="Normal">"Vic nng hay nh khng nn xem xt  mt khi lng m hy xem xt v mt kin thc. Chnh kin thc nng quyt nh vic hc sinh c phi mang sch v nhiu hay khng", PGS Cng ni.</p>\r\n<p class="Normal">T phn tch ny, tc gi ca b sch gio khoa Ton ph thng hin hnh gp , vic mang sch v nh i vi tr nh l khng cn thit. Sch c th   lp v hc sinh ch cn v tay khng, hm sau li n hc tip. Vi hc sinh cp 2, thi gian hc  nh ch nn 30-45 pht mi ngy v ch lm bi tp ming ch khng phi vit. V theo PGS Cng, gii php tt nht  hc sinh khng phi mang cp nng l gim ti chng trnh hc.</p>\r\n<p class="Normal">Rt ng tnh vi quan im ny, thy Nguyn K Ho cho rng tht bt hp l khi bui ti ngi ln i chi cn tr con phi ngi hc. "Ton x hi phi cng chung tay, ng, Nh nc cng cn c nh hng. Ti ch mong cc chu c hc nh nhng, pht trin bnh thng, khng g p", thy Ho tm s.</p>\r\n<p class="Normal">Hiu trng Cao Th Hng  xut mt gii php n gin v ang c trng thc hin l hng dn hc sinh  sch v li ngn bn  lp hc.  m bo an ton, mi lp cng c giao mt kha ca ring. Hng ngy cc chu ch cn mang cun sch gio khoa no cn son bi v nh  c trc, cn v chnh t, tp lm vn, ghi u bi... u  li trng.</p>\r\n<p class="Normal">"Cui tun nu b m mun kim tra v ca con th c gio s pht mang v", c Hng ni v cho hay, thi thong phi mang cn n tng lp kim tra t xut cn nng cp ca hc sinh. Nu em no phi mang qu nng th  ngh gio vin ch nhim nhc nh ph huynh kp thi.</p>\r\n<p class="Normal" align="right"><strong>vnexpress</strong></p>\r\n</div>', '', 1, 25, 0, 135, '2011-11-19 14:27:15', 62, '', '2011-12-06 06:34:37', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-11-19 14:25:33', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 8, 0, 1, '', '', 0, 24, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(56, 'Tr chi dn gian: Tp tm vng', 'tro-chi-dan-gian-tp-tm-vong', '', '<p style="text-align: left;"><strong><strong><span style="font-family: Arial;">\r\n<table style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" align="left" border="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style="font-size: 8pt;"> <br /></span></td>\r\n<td><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><img src="http://e-cadao.com/images/thadiababa.gif" width="235" border="0" height="111" /></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</span></strong></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times;">Bi ng dao ny ph bin khp Bc, Trung, Nam nhi theo m trng tm vng (gi theo Ngh An) tc trng cm:</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times;">Cch chi hin nay ca tr ny l hai ngui chi ngi i mt nhau, va ht va theo nhp p lng bn tay vo nhau: hoc p thng, hoc p cho, hoc mt cao mt h thp, hoc kt hp nhiu cch khc nhau. Ni chung, cch chi rt ging tr Tha la tha ly y.</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n<table style="width: 324px; height: 128px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" id="table6" border="0" cellpadding="4" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top" width="50%">\r\n<p style="margin-left: 5px;"><span style="font-size: 8pt; color: #ff6600;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">Tp tm vng<br />Ch c chng<br />Em  v<br />Ch n c,<br />Em mt xng.<br /><span style="font-size: 8pt; color: #ff6600;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">Ch n ko,<br />Em n cm</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign="top" width="50%">\r\n<p style="margin-left: 5px;"><span style="font-size: 8pt; color: #ff6600;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">...<br />Ch  L Gm,<br />Em  Bn Thnh.<br />Ch trng hnh, <br />Em trng h.<br />Chi nui m<br />Em nui cha</span></span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><br /></span></p>', '', 1, 25, 0, 134, '2011-11-24 07:20:10', 62, '', '2011-11-24 13:41:37', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-11-24 07:19:12', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '', 5, 0, 1, '', '', 0, 20, ''),
(57, 'Nhng im ni bt ca mt gio vin gii', 'nhng-im-ni-bt-ca-mt-giao-vien-gii', '', '<div style="font-weight: bold; padding: 10px 10px 10px 0pt; color: #4c4a4a; text-align: justify;">\r\n<table align="left" border="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://conduongmoi.com.vn/upload/news/Giao%20vien%20gioi.jpg" height="235" width="314" border="0" /></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<span style="font-size: 8pt;">Nhiu nghin cu v nhiu nh gio dc u tin rng mt yu t <span class="IL_AD" id="IL_AD4">quan trng nht  xc nh cht lng ca gio dc c th hin  cht lng ca gio vin.</span></span></div>\r\n<div style="padding: 10px 10px 10px 0pt;">\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">Vy gio vin cht lng hay gio vin gii c nhng c im g? Ngh dy hc l mt trong nhng ngh phc tp nht ngy&nbsp; nay. N yu cu gio vin phi c mt khi lng kin thc v mc tiu, bi ging v h tiu chun; nim am m vi ngh, thi  r rng v ngh nghip v tinh thn hc hi; phi c kin thc v nhng nguyn tc v k nng qun l lp hc; v c khao kht to ra s <span class="IL_AD" id="IL_AD6">thay i ln trong cuc sng ca tr. Vi tt c nhng yu cu  th  tr thnh mt gio vin gii qu thc rt kh.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong>* Di y l mt s c tnh ca mt gio vin gii:</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">- Gio vin gii lun t ra s k vng cao vi tt c hc sinh ca mnh: H thng k vng mi hc sinh trong lp c th v s nhn c ton b kin thc, k nng m c ging trn lp, v h khng bao gi t b mc tiu  vi nhng hc sinh cha t c kt qu tt</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">- Gio vin gii lun c nhng mc tiu r rng trong gio n: Nhng gio vin ging dy hiu qu l nhng ngi lun c k hoch bi ging  <span class="IL_AD" id="IL_AD7">cung cp <span class="IL_AD" id="IL_AD3">cho hc sinh nhng  tng r rng v iu g tr s c hc, s c giao bi tp th no v c tuyn dng khi hon thnh ra sao. Bi tp  lun c mc tiu hc tp v bi tp  lun a cho hc sinh nhiu c hi  thc hnh k nng mi. Gio vin cng lun a ra mt cch thc chm im n nh v dng bi tp c lp i lp li.</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">- Gio vin gii l ngi lun chun b tt v c tm th sn sng: H l nhng ngi lun n lp hc sm v sn sng ging dy.&nbsp; H trnh by bi hc mt cch r rng v c trnh t. Lp hc c t chc mt cch khoa hc v hn ch ti a nhng yu t lm t qung bi ging.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">- Gio vin gii lun bit khuyn khch hc sinh v gip hc sinh nhn nhn mt vn  trong nhiu cch khc nhau: H s dng thc t nh l mt im khi u ch khng phi l im kt thc; h lun t cu hi Ti sao, nhn vo mi kha cnh v khuyn khch hc sinh d on v iu g tip tc s xy ra. H thng xuyn t ra nhng cu hi   chc chn rng hc sinh vn ang i <span class="IL_AD" id="IL_AD5">theo mc tiu ca bi ging. H c gng pht <span class="IL_AD" id="IL_AD1">huy ton b cc thnh vin trong lp v trnh tuyt i khng  mt s hc sinh thng tr lp hc. H duy trnh s khch l hc sinh bng nhng cch tip cn trc tip v khc nhau.</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">- Gio vin gii l nhng ngi c quan h rt tt vi hc sinh v h phi cho thy hc sinh no cng c nh vy: Mt gio vin gii l ngi nhit tnh, d gn, am m v c trch nhim vi cng vic. Nhng gio vin c bit n vi nhng c im ny chnh l nhng ngi thng  li lp mun  chi vi tr v trao i thng tin vi ph huynh khi h cn. H nhit tnh tham gia cc hot ng cng ng ca nh trng v th hin s cam kt gn b vi nh trng.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">- Mt gio vin gii l ngi phi lm ch c nhng mc tiu: H th hin c s rnh mch trong mc tiu bi ging v ginh thi gian  hc thm nhng kin thc lin quan n lnh vc h ging dy. H th hin gio c trc quan ca bi ging mt cch cn thn, t m v truyn th c s ham mun hc hi nhiu hn vn  gio vin a ra.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">- Gio vin gii l ngi thng xuyn trao i thng tin vi ph huynh: H tip cn vi ph huynh thng qua cc chng trnh hi tho v thng xuyn ghi nht k gi v nh cho ph huynh. H khng ngi ngn cm in thoi gi cho ph huynh nu h thy ph huynh ang quan tm n con h.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong>* Nhng du hiu ca mt gio vin khng c nng lc:</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">- Hc sinh lun phn nn rng gio vin lun lun a ra nhng nhn xt khng tch cc v tr.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">- Gio vin lun l ngi n mun nht lp vo bui sng v ri lp u tin vo bui chiu. Khng tr li in thoi ca ph huynh hoc khng tr li th ca ph huynh.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">- Hc sinh rt t khi mang bi tp v nh.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">- Bi tp v nh thng khng c thu li hoc khng c gio vin trao i li vi hc sinh</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">- Gio vin khng gi s nht k hoc trao i thng tin vi ph huynh</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">- Gio vin th hin s hn ch v kin thc ca bi ging m mnh ging dy.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">- Bi ging thiu k hoch v khng c cu trc, trnh t r rng.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">- Gio vin t chi chp nhn bt k ng gp no ca ph huynh.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong>Thc s Nguyn Thnh on<br />Hiu trng H thng trng Mm non Hong Gia. </strong></span></p>\r\n</div>', '', 1, 25, 0, 135, '2011-11-24 07:28:52', 62, '', '2011-12-06 06:35:42', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-11-24 07:23:48', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 2, 0, 4, '', '', 0, 9, 'robots=\nauthor=');
