(40, 'K nim Ngy nh gio Vit Nam 20/11/2011: Cnh n nh lm nn nhng ma xun', 'k-nim-ngay-nha-giao-vit-nam-20112011-canh-en-nh-lam-nen-nhng-mua-xuan', '', '<p></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="summary">Chy bng am m bi dng hc sinh gii cho t nc, hn 30 nm qua, c L Th Dung (sinh nm 1959), gio vin mn Sinh hc Trng THPT chuyn H Ni - Amsterdam lun cn mn, sng to trong dy hc.</p>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;">\r\n<div align="justify">\r\n<table style="width: 100%;" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>\r\n<p class="storyInlinePhoto"><img src="http://giadinh.vcmedia.vn/Images/Uploaded/Share/2011/11/18/canhen.jpg" width="95%" /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p align="center">C gio L Th Dung vinh d nhn Bng khen ca UBND TP H Ni. nh: Q.Huy</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div align="justify">Bn duyn vi ngh</div>\r\n<div align="justify"><br />Sinh ra v ln ln ti H Ni, qua 31 nm ng trn bc ging, i vi c gio L Th Kim Dung ngh dy hc nh mt duyn s, bi thu cn cp sch ti trng, c lun c m c c lm ngh y, cu gip ngi bnh. C Dung nh li: "Hi cn hc lp 10 trng THPT Ty Sn (H Ni), ti l mt hc sinh c kt qu hc tp tt, li hay gip  cc bn trong lp v hc tp. Lc , thy gio ch nhim khuyn nn chn ngh s phm v c nng lc s phm. Cng thch s phm, nhng ti li mun theo ngnh y v d nh thi vo H Y. Tuy nhin, mt bn thn trong lp khuyn rng ngh y khng ph hp, nn sau mt thi gian suy ngh, nm 18 tui, ti  chn thi vo H S phm H Ni 1".</div>\r\n<div align="justify"><br />Tt nghip H vi tm bng s phm, khoa Sinh hc nm 1980, c Dung bt u s nghip ca mnh  Trng THPT Ninh Thanh (tnh Hi Hng c).  nng cao chuyn mn, c quyt nh hc cao hc ti khoa Sinh, H S phm t nm 1984-1986. Nm 1987, vi trnh  thc s, c  trng tuyn vo Trng THPT chuyn H Ni - Amsterdam. Khi y, c l mt trong nhng gio vin tr nht trng. Lc y, nh trng  c rt nhiu gio vin gii ca H Ni, trong  nhiu gio vin rt giu kinh nghim.</div>\r\n<div align="justify">Theo c Dung,  chnh l may mn trong s nghip ca mnh, c tr v H Ni lm vic gn gia nh v mt mi trng lm vic thun li khi o to ra cc th h hc sinh gii cho thnh ph v t nc. C Dung chia s,  mi trng , c may mn c cc nh gio c thm nin nh thy  Thin Ngon, ri thy o Thin Khi lun gip   mt gio vin tr nh c c c c hi pht trin. Vi c,  l c hi m ra  c gio cha n 30 tui say m, tn tm vi ngh, vi nhng th h hc sinh xut sc ca Th .</div>\r\n<div align="justify">"Bi thu" hc sinh gii</div>\r\n<div align="justify">\r\n<table style="width: 100%;" align="right">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p align="justify">Trong L k nim ngy Nh gio Vit Nam 20/11 v Tuyn dng khen thng cc in hnh tin tin, nh gio mu mc nm hc 2010-2011 do S GD&T H Ni t chc, c gio L Th Dung (Trng THPT chuyn H Ni-Amsterdam)  vinh d n nhn Bng khen ca UBND TP H Ni v c nhiu thnh tch trong ging dy, bi dng hc sinh gii mn Sinh hc, vi 36 gii quc gia, 6 gii quc t. Ngoi ra, nhiu nm lin c t danh hiu Chin s thi ua cp c s, Ngi tt vic tt cp thnh ph</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div align="justify">31 nm tn tm vi ngh, theo c Dung, i vi vic bi dng hc sinh gii, u tin l phi tuyn chn cc em t lc mi vo lp 10. y l cc em "c bit" nn phng php truyn th cng c nt ring bit. Mi lp hc cng ch c 5-10 em hc gii. i vi cc em ny, phi ln k hoch  ch bo cc em t hc. nh hng cc em chn lc thng tin, tm c sch lin quan, nm c mu cht ca kin thc c bn t  mi n cc kin thc nng cao. Phi hng dn cc em lm  cng tng phn, sau  kim tra gip cc em hc hc th no cho tt hn.</div>\r\n<div align="justify"><br />Cng vic bi dng hc sinh gii, nht l i tuyn i thi quc t cng rt vt v.  c mt tit dy trn lp, c phi mt nhiu thi gian cho vic son gio n, tm ti liu, tranh nh minh ha cho bi hc thm sinh ng. Ngoi ra, phi tng hp cc kin thc t cc ti liu, sch gio khoa  cc nc do cc hc sinh c mua tng, t  gii thiu cho cc em tip cn vi cc chng trnh tin tin.</div>\r\n<div align="justify"> khc phc nhng tit hc kh khan, c Dung  p dng cc phng tin, dy theo knh hnh, hnh nh p, ng, ly  trn mng  cc em cm nhn v yu thch. Ni dung bi hc phi c ng, c bn. Phi lin h thc t, mi bi dy phi c mt cu chuyn nh ch vi pht cho bi hc c tnh thc tin. C nh th, cc em khng thy mt mi, sau mi bi hc, cc em thy thch th hn.</div>\r\n<div align="justify"><br />Phn ln cc em hc chuyn Sinh u i theo ngnh y, sau ny tr thnh bc s hoc ging vin... Nhng c vn lo lng khi nhiu em hin nay th  vi ngh s phm, lo tng lai i ng gio vin gii ngy cng t i. Hc sinh ca c ginh ti 36 gii quc gia, 6 gii quc t, nhng theo c Dung, cc em vn cn nhiu thit thi, bi trang thit b phng th nghim cn thiu thn. Cc em nm rt chc kin thc, nhng hn ch trong thc hnh dn n vic ginh huy chng s gp rt nhiu kh khn.</div>\r\n<div align="justify"><br />C Dung chia s: "Ti c c may mn v thun li trong cng vic  l c dy cc em hc sinh gii. Bn cnh  l s s chia, gip  ca chng ti, cng l gio vin gii dy mn Vt l cng trng. Thm na l s gip  ca cc ph huynh, thy c ca mt s trng H". Tht ng trn trng v t ho i vi nhng tm gng nh gio sng bnh d, tm huyt vi s nghip "trng ngi" nh c Dung v bao gio vin khc lun ht mnh v cc th h hc sinh hm nay v mai sau.</div>\r\n<div align="right">Ng Quang Huy</div>\r\n</div>', '', 1, 24, 0, 118, '2011-11-19 14:35:54', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-11-19 14:34:45', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '', 1, 0, 2, '', '', 0, 38, ''),
(41, '30 triu cho bi vit gng ngi tt, gii php gio dc', '30-triu-cho-bai-vit-gng-ngi-tt-gii-phap-giao-dc', '', '<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Truyn ngn cn bm 2 ni dung: vit v s nghip i mi ca ngnh gio dc-o to m nhn vt trung tm l nh gio, nh trng, hc sinh v sinh vin</strong></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><br /> Vit truyn ngn, phng s, bt k nu gng ngi tt hoc phn nh vn , nu ra gii php trong gio dc s c nhn thng cao nht 30 triu ng.</p>\r\n<p align="justify">Chiu 24/3, B GD-T phi hp vi Hi Nh vn Vit Nam, Hi Nh bo Vit Nam, Cng on Gio dc Vit Nam v Nh Xut bn Gio dc Vit Nam pht ng cuc thi Truyn ngn, bt k, phng s v ngnh gio dc.<br /> <br /> Truyn ngn cn bm 2 ni dung: vit v s nghip i mi ca ngnh gio dc-o to m nhn vt trung tm l nh gio, nh trng, hc sinh v sinh vin; mi quan h hu c gia nh trng, gia nh v x hi trong vic gio dc-o to th h tr tr thnh nhng ch nhn tng lai ca t nc.</p>\r\n<div style="text-align: right;" align="center">\r\n<table style="border-width: medium; border-style: none; border-color: -moz-use-text-color; background: none repeat scroll 0% 0% #ccffcc; border-collapse: collapse; width: 355px; height: 306px;" border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr style="height: 229pt;">\r\n<td style="padding: 0in 5.4pt; border-width: 1pt; border-style: solid; border-color: windowtext; width: 248.85pt; height: 229pt; background-color: transparent;" valign="top" width="332">\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Ngy 20/3, Ph Th tng kim B trng B GD-T Nguyn Thin Nhn  k Quyt nh s 1046, v vic thnh lp Ban Ch o v Ban T chc cuc thi Truyn ngn, bt k, phng s v ngnh gio dc.</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Theo , thnh phn Ban Ch o gm: Th trng B GD-T Phm V Lun (trng ban). Hai ph trng ban gm Ch tch Hi Nh vn Vit Nam Hu Thnh v Ph Ch tch thng trc Hi Nh bo Vit Nam L Quc Trung.</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">ng Ng Trn i, Tng G Nh Xut bn Vit Nam lm Ph Trng ban thng trc.</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Trng Ban T chc cuc thi l ng Nguyn Minh Khang, Ph Tng Gim c Nh xut bn Gio dc Vit Nam. Hai ph trng ban gm ng Vn nh ng, Ph Chnh Vn phng B GD-T v ng Nguyn Tr Hun, Ph Ch tch Hi Nh vn Vit Nam, Tng Bin tp bo Vn Ngh.</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p align="justify">Yu cu vi bt k, phng s l biu dng kp thi nhng c nhn, n v, cc c s gio dc t thnh tch xut sc trong phong tro thi ua "hai tt" (Dy tt - Hc tt), trong vic thc hin cuc vn ng Mi thy gio, c gio l mt tm gng o c, t hc v sng to.</p>\r\n<p align="justify">Ngoi ra, c th nh nhng vn  ca hin nay, nu vn  vi  thc xy dng v ch ra hng gii quyt.</p>\r\n<p align="justify">Cng dn Vit Nam c th d thi nhiu nht l 5 tc phm, gi v: Ban T chc cuc thi "Truyn ngn, bt k, phng s v ngnh gio dc"  81 Trn Hng o, qun Hon Kim, H Ni.</p>\r\n<p align="justify">Bi d thi di khng qu 5.000 t, cha ng ti trn bo ch; tc gi ghi r tn, a ch, s in thoi vo t giy ring nh km bi vit</p>\r\n<p align="justify">Ban T chc cho bit, ngoi gii nht 30 triu ng, gii nh 20 triu ng; gii ba 10 triu ng, s c gii khuyn khch 5 triu ng. S lng gii thng do ban t chc quyt nh. Cc bi vit s ng ti trn mt s bo v tp ch; ng thi c xut bn thnh sch  s dng trong cc trng hc.</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p class="textbody" align="right">Theo VNN</p>\r\n<p align="right"><i>Theo <b>www.ktdt.com.vn</b></i></p>', '', 1, 26, 0, 131, '2011-11-19 14:37:35', 62, '', '2011-11-20 19:51:13', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-11-19 14:37:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '', 3, 0, 3, '', '', 0, 25, ''),
(42, 'Hc Bc, mi ngi lm mt vic tt', 'hc-bac-mi-ngi-lam-mt-vic-tt', '', '<p style="text-align: justify;"><b>Hn hai nm qua, Qung Nam cng c nc thu c nhiu kt qu trong Cuc vn ng Hc tp v lm theo tm gng o c H Ch Minh v thc hin Di chc ca Ngi. Cng hc tp Bc, chng ta thy t tng, o c, phong cch v tm gng ca Ngi cng ngi sng,...</b>\r\n<table style="width: 1px;" align="center" border="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="http://baoquangnam.com.vn/images/2009/t9/1/hb2909.jpg" alt="alt" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="text-align: center;"><i>Hi thi K chuyn v tm gng o c H Ch Minh ca Cng an tnh.</i></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">iu v cng qu gi mang li t cuc vn ng l  mi lnh vc ca cuc sng, ca cng vic cng hin din li dy ca Bc. V trong thc t, c rt nhiu tm gng in hnh, ngi tt - vic tt  din ra khp ni, vi nhng vic lm c th, nhng sc lan ta li su rng, cm ha c nhiu ngi</p>\r\n', '\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Mt bui tra thng by nng gt, c Nguyn Vn Nng (83 tui,  t 3, khi ph Xun Quang, phng Tn An, TP. Hi An) khi nghe c ngi cn xem phng trng by hin vt truyn thng v Bc H l gic ngay a chu du c ra nh vn ha thn m ca, mng r gii thiu ngay vi mi ngi Tng l lnh trn on tu khng s vt bin a v kh vo Nam, tr v cng tcthi gian di trong ngnh gio dc, c Nng lun quan tm n vic bi dng  thc cch mng, nng cao tinh thn yu nc, lng t ho v truyn thng v lch s ca dn tc cho qun chng nhn dn v lp tr. Chnh c t su tm, chn lc, trng by nhiu tranh nh, tc phm th vn v Bc H, v cc k i hi ng ton quc, v cc mc son lch s ca dn tc, v ni dung xy dng i sng vn ha Nhng dp h, l lt, khu vn ha Xun Quang nh vy  tr thnh t im sinh hot b ch. Sng chan ha, thng yu bn tr, c Nng lun tm ti, sng to, t chc nhiu hot ng, nhiu hnh thc sinh hot mi l nh k chuyn,  vui, trang tr tm hiu v lch s Vit Nam, v vng t, v danh nhn vn ha Qung Nam, Hi An thu ht ng o thanh thiu nhi khi ph tham gia. iu ng ghi nhn v trn trng i vi c Nguyn Vn Nng l tinh thn ch cng v t, hy sinh li ch ring v li ch ca cng ng. C  dnh dm tin tit kim, ng h gn 16 triu ng  lo cho nhiu chuyn ca khi ph nh t chc hi thi, tu sa trang thit b hot ng, thu xe  t chng ngp ng ng ph, gp mua ti vi cho gia nh kh khn, ng t, mua sch xy th vin</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Cng cm hng knh yu lnh t, dnh nhiu s chm lo cho cc th h tng lai ca t nc nh c Nguyn Vn Nng,  khi ph Long Xuyn c c Hunh Ngc Trng nay  tui 84 nhng vn say m su tp ti liu, lm lch treo tng, i ni chuyn v Bc H cho chi b, hc sinh nghe; ng vin mi ngi, mi ngy nn sng v hc tp, lm theo gng Bc. C Trng quan nim yu Bc H tht gin d: C i ngi  hy sinh tt c cho t nc cho dn tc, ti mun hnh nh Ngi hm nay ti vui, sinh ng,  con chu thy Ngi tht gn, tht gin d m knh yu, m hc tp gng Ngi. Nhng tp lch c o, p gin d v Bc H m ng c t m dy cng th hin trong nhiu nm qua c sc lan ta m thm m ln lao, truyn ti n nhiu ngi, nhiu th h cn b, ng vin, thanh thiu nin ni c sinh sng nhiu bi hc qu gi. Ring c Trng, bi hc ln nht c hc c t Bc l bn cht sng ngi ca anh B i C H - bn thn c rt lc quan a gia nh vt qua bit bao nhc nhn kh khn  n nh cuc sng. ng c ni: i ti c Bc soi ng, sng vi Bc ngy no, ti thy tinh thn ti vui, sng khoi ngy .</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Nhiu nm ri, lng tt l lng ca bc s Nguyn Ngc Tho (Bnh vin a khoa Duy Xuyn) l ni nng ta ca rt nhiu th h hc sinh, sinh vin ngho v ngi gp bt hnh. Bc s  ln li n vng su, vng xa tm kim ngi c nh, i au cu mang v a thng tin ln mng ku gi lng tt ca mi ngi... Lng tt ca ng khng ch gip ngt c nhiu ngi m cn gip h t tin, c gng vt qua khn kh v mt l: khng th li bc v s ph tm lng  tng nng  ca nhng ngi tt nh ng.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Vi nm trc,  xm ngho thuc x Bnh Tr (huyn Thng Bnh) c mt c hc tr lm bnh n thp t nht sinh, ch bit nm ch cht. Trong cn cng qun, c b vit bc th tuyt mnh. ng V Tn Hiu lc  l cn b ca y ban Dn s gia nh tr em huyn Thng Bnh  ln li ngy m i g ca khp ni  xin ti tr hn 50 triu ng a em i Hu m tim. Ca m din ra sun s, c b m yu ngy trc bc vo i hc, gi tr thnh cn b mt trng THCS  qu nh... Gi y, ng V Tn Hiu khng cn cng tc  n v c, nhng lc no ngi ta cng thy ng bn bu, trn tr vi hng trm s phn hc tr ngho, ngi bt hnh mc bnh him ngho, li g ca khp ni nh gip  cho nhng ngi khng quen bit. ng Hiu quan nim: thy ngi lm cnh bt hnh, ti thy y ny lng tm, nn phi tm cch gip.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Khng th k ht nhng ngi vi nhng vic lm bnh thng, gin d nh th ang ngy m cng hin, gip  cho cng ng. iu  c sc mnh lan ta su xa, l minh chng cho sc sng bt dit ca t tng H Ch Minh. Nh li ca PGS. TS o Duy Qut trong hi ngh tuyn dng c nhn in hnh lm theo gng Bc  pha Nam: H  c nhng hnh ng, vic l lm theo tm gng Bc rt c th t hiu qu cao, c mi ngi dn xung quanh v cc cp y, chnh quyn ghi nhn. Tuy mi ngi c mt cch lm khc nhau song h  t bn tiu ch o c chnh khi hc tp v lm theo tm gng o c ca Bc.  l: ton tm, ton  thc hin trch nhim ca mnh, ht lng, ht sc vi cng vic; yu thng ng bo; tit kim; khng tham nhng v chng tham nhng</p>\r\n<p>Ti tr s UBND x Tam Dn, huyn Ph Ninh, ng y, UBND x dnh ring mt khong khng gian rt thun tin cho ngi xem  treo hn 100 bc nh c cc bc cu chin binh ca x su tm mt cch ht sc cng phu. S nh trn c sp xp ng vo hai khung ln vi 2 ch  l: S tht v chin tranh Vit Nam v Cuc khng chin chng Php- M ca dn tc.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n<table style="width: 1px;" align="center" border="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="http://www.baoquangnam.com.vn/images/2009/t9/1/hbb_2909.jpg" height="375" width="500" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="text-align: center;"><i>ng Phan Ch Cng, Ph B th ng y x Tam Dn gii thiu v phng trng by.</i></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br />ng Phan Ch Cng, Ph B th thng trc ng y x Tam Dn cho bit: Hc theo Bc, ci g c li cho dn th ht sc lm, ci g c hi cho dn th ht sc trnh. Nhng hnh nh v ti c qun th, v cuc khng chin cu nc c trng by l cch thc  nhc nh v ci gi phi tr cho c lp t do cho T quc.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Nhiu nm qua x Tam Dn l mt trong s cc a phng dn u vic thc hin cng tc n n p ngha ca huyn Ph Ninh, t chc c s ng c cng nhn trong sch vng mnh.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong>GD&T</strong></span></p>', 1, 26, 0, 131, '2011-11-19 14:40:23', 62, '', '2011-11-20 19:44:32', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-11-19 14:39:38', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '', 3, 0, 1, '', '', 0, 46, ''),
(55, 'Mt s tr chi dy tr ng x tt', 'mt-s-tro-chi-dy-tr-ng-x-tt', '', '<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong>Tr ng vai s gip&nbsp;tr thng cm c ni bun ca ngi khc, hay chi ct dn on tu s dy&nbsp;tr tnh kin nhn... Tham kho cc tr chi n gin di y, bn s ngc nhin v s hiu qu ca chng.</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong><span style="color: #008000;">1. Tr chi: Lp mt on tu</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n<table style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; width: 298px; height: 279px;" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="http://www.vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A0/CB/16/hop.jpg" height="229" width="274" border="1" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style="color: #008080;">Vic ct, dn, lp on tu s dy b tnh kin nhn.</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><em><span style="text-decoration: underline;">a.Cch chi:<br /></span></em> Bn cn vi ci v hp rng  ln  b ngi vo trong. Chun b cc ph liu  ct dn, v dy mt b cch  bin ci hp ca mnh thnh mt <span class="IL_AD" id="IL_AD1">toa tu. Sau khi tr c gng trang tr chic hp vi bnh xe, ca s v bt c th g&nbsp;tr ngh ra, bn hy gip b ni tng toa vi nhau.</span><em><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><br />b. Tc dng:<br /></span></em>Tr chi ny dy tr tnh kin nhn. Tr chi ny yu cu tr nhiu cng on chun b, v n s mang li cho&nbsp;tr s thch th sau khi t c thnh qu.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong><span style="color: #008000;">2. Tr chi:&nbsp;&nbsp;Ti tnh ln no</span></strong></span>\r\n<table style="float: left; width: 227px; height: 252px;" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="http://www.vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A0/CB/16/hop2.jpg" height="202" width="202" border="1" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style="font-size: 8pt; color: #008080;">Tr bt chc nhng khun mt trn giy gip&nbsp;tr bit cch cm thn</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><em></em></span><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><em>a. <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Cch chi:</span></em> </span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">Trn nhng t giy vung c ln, v mt lot nhng khun mt vi sc thi khng vui khc nhau - bun, gin d, m, hong s. t cc t giy vo mt ci r v yu cu l tr ln lt chn mt khun mt v th hin cm xc theo khun mt . Chng hn mt a tr "bun" c th gi v khc. V nhim v ca nhng a khc l phi gip bn n ti tnh ln. u tin, chng nn hi cc cu "Sao bn li bun? T c th lm g gip bn by gi?". Sau khi a tr nhp vai gii thch "Bn t c  vi t" - nhng a tr khc s a ra gii php, nh v vai, v ni "t rt tic" hoc <span class="IL_AD" id="IL_AD3">chia s mt mu bnh.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" align="justify"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><em><span style="text-decoration: underline;">b. Tc dng:<br /></span></em>Tr ny dy tr s cm thng v tm quan trng ca vic tn trng cng nh tt bng vi ngi khc.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong><span style="color: #008000;">3. Tr chi : Gn hoc Xa</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><em></em><em><span style="text-decoration: underline;">a.Cch chi:</span></em></span><br /><span style="font-size: 8pt;">Chn mt a tr ng vai "ngi tm kim".  ngh&nbsp;tr ra khi phng trong khi cc&nbsp;tr khc giu mt  vt i, nh mt qu bng ,  u  trong phng. Gi "ngi tm kim" tr li v  ngh i tm qu bng, trong khi nhng&nbsp;tr khc ku ln nhng gi  "cu ang n gn" hay "cu ang i xa". Chi cho n khi tm thy  vt, v bt u li vi "ngi tm kim" mi.<em><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><br />b. Tc dng:<br /></span></em>Tr ny dy tr s hp tc.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong><span style="color: #008000;">4. Tr chi :Ti l gin ip</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><em></em><em><span style="text-decoration: underline;">a.Cch chi:<br /></span></em>Ln lt cc&nbsp;tr chn mt vt  gn mnh v m t: "Bng i mt t hon ca mnh t nhn thy mt th g  mu xanh l cy...".&nbsp;Tr khc s c gng on xem vt  l g "Mt ci cy!" "Qun i ca b!"... Ai on ng s c lm "gin ip" tip theo.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><em><span style="text-decoration: underline;">b. Tc dng:<br /></span></em>Tr chi ny dy tr tnh kin nhn. Tr ny cng c ch trong nhng chuyn i chi di hoc xa, nh trn mt chuyn bay di.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong><span style="color: #008000;">5. Tr chi :"Xin php m"</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><em></em><em><span style="text-decoration: underline;">a.Cch chi:<br /></span></em>Xp hng cc tr mun chi trc mt bn, cch khong 3 mt. Ra lnh vi mt&nbsp;tr "Bn Mai, bc ln pha trc mt bc". Nu&nbsp;Mai p li "Xin php m", bn c th ni, "c, con c php" hoc "khng, con khng c php".</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">Nu li p ca bn l "c", hy chc chn rng b&nbsp;Mai s ni "cm n" trc khi bc ln. Nu b no qun xin php hoc cm n th s b quay tr li vch xut pht. Tip tc chi cho n khi mt b khc bc n v tr ca "M". V b  s c c hi ng vai m.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><em><span style="text-decoration: underline;">b. Tc dng:<br /></span></em>Tr ny dy tr s tn trng. Nh phi gii thch r rng lut chi vi tr  trnh nhm ln.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong><span style="color: #008000;">6.Tr&nbsp; chi: Ni s tht</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><em><span style="text-decoration: underline;">a.Cch chi:</span></em> </span><br /><span style="font-size: 8pt;">Khi c gia nh quy qun, hy  cho tt c mi ngi c c hi kt thc cu "Ti  tng s hi khi...". B v m c th bt u tr chi bng cch k chuyn ca chnh mnh ("B tng s hi khi Tm bin mt trong ca hng v b khng th tm thy"). Sau khi  ht lt c nh, hy lp li tr chi nhng bng mt sc thi tnh cm mi, chng hn "vui" hay "ngc nhin".</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><em><span style="text-decoration: underline;">b. Tc dng:<br /></span></em>Tr ny dy tr s thnh thc, v tr cng s cm thy an ton khi ni ra s thc.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong><span style="color: #008000;">7. Tr chi: Xp bt&nbsp;tt</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n<table style="width: 224px; height: 318px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="http://www.vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A0/CB/16/hop3.jpg" height="440" width="330" border="1" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Tr chi xp tt dy b tnh trch nhim.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><em><span style="text-decoration: underline;">a.Cch chi:<br /></span></em>khi xp li t qun o, hy dn ht nhng chic tt sang mt bn. Tri chng xung nn nh v nh b tm tt theo i. Khi&nbsp;tr  chn xong, dy tr cch cun mi i tt thnh mt qu bng. Sau , lm vi chic hp ng tt, mi hp ghi tn mt thnh vin trong gia nh.&nbsp;Tr s phi th ng tt ca ai v hp ca ngi y.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><em><span style="text-decoration: underline;">b. Tc dng:<br /></span></em>Tr ny s dy tr tnh trch nhim. Nh khen ngi&nbsp;tr  lm tt, v c th ln sau tr s xin c gp qun o na.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong>8<span style="color: #008000;">. Tr chi: Bi hc v ging ni</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<table style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; width: 244px; height: 355px;" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="http://www.vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3B/A0/CB/16/hop4.jpg" height="428" width="322" border="1" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td> tr nghe li ghi m ca chnh mnh khi vui v, khi m nheo...</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><em><span style="text-decoration: underline;">a.Cch chi:</span></em> </span><br /><span style="font-size: 8pt;">c 10 cu t mt cun sch tr em vo mt cun bng, s dng xen k ging ni d chu v ging ni m nheo, than vn. Bt chng li cho tr nghe v yu cu&nbsp;tr gi tay ln khi nghe thy cc cu c ging ni d chu. Khi&nbsp;tr lm ng, hy cho b c ghi m ging mnh  trng thi ng ngn nht, m nheo nht v d thng nht.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><em><span style="text-decoration: underline;">b. Tc dng:<br /></span></em>Tr ny dy cho&nbsp;tr &nbsp;thy m nheo chng hay ho cht no.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong>(Ngun: vnexpress)</strong><br /></span></p>', '', 1, 25, 0, 135, '2011-11-24 07:15:35', 62, '', '2011-12-06 06:35:55', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-11-24 07:13:27', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 9, 0, 5, '', '', 0, 21, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(44, 'K nim Ngy Nh gio Vit Nam 20-11: Tn vinh gi tr ngi thy', 'k-nim-ngay-nha-giao-vit-nam-20-11-ton-vinh-gia-tr-ngi-thy', '', '<p style="text-align: justify;" class="summary">&nbsp;Hng ti ngy Hin chng cc nh gio Vit Nam 20-11-2011, trong nhng ngy qua, nhiu a phng trn c nc  lin tc t chc nhng hot ng nhm tn vinh gi tr ngh dy hc. T min ni n thnh th, hoc vng su, vng xa, ni bin cng hi o u rn rng cho n ngy l trng i ny: ngy l tn vinh nhng tm gng cao c, cng hin ht mnh cho s nghip trng ngi.</p>\r\n<p class="storyInlinePhoto"><em><img style="float: left;" src="http://daidoanket.vn/Pictures/bao%20tuan/_2011/276/2011_276_3_IMG_0757.jpg" height="255" width="351" /></em></p>\r\n<p align="justify">&nbsp;<em></em>Nm hc 2011-2012 l nm nh du nhiu s thay i ln trong ngnh gio dc. Tuy s nh hng, i mi trong ngnh cn gp phi rt nhiu kh khn, th thch, nhng nhn chung mi n lc ca B GD&amp;T u hng ti mc tiu tch cc nhm nng cao cht lng o to; nng cao i sng gio vin; p dng nhiu chnh sch u i; tip tc trin khai nhiu cuc vn ng  ngha nhm to mt mi trng gio dc lnh mnh, cht lng, bn vng.</p>\r\n<p align="justify">Thc hin Ngh quyt ca ng, Nh nc, Quc hi, B GD&amp;T  mnh dn a ra nhiu quyt sch, nh p dng ph cp thm nin cho gio vin; ch  i ng i vi gio vin min ni, vng su, vng xa; xy dng d tho Lut Gio dc i hc; i mi phng thc dy v hc  cc cp hc, gim ti chng trnh sch gio khoa; chnh l b sung quy ch tuyn sinh... Tt c nhm ci cch, i mi h thng gio dc - o to cho thch ng vi yu cu v s pht trin ca x hi. c bit, vo dp k nim Ngy Nh gio Vit Nam, nhiu hot ng tn vinh gi tr ngh dy hc din ra cng lm cho x hi thm tin tng, c v, ng thun trc nhng tm gng n lc v s nghip trng ngi m nhng thy c ang ngy m cng hin.</p>\r\n', '\r\n<table style="width: 100%;" align="right">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p align="justify"><em>Nhn L tuyn dng cc in hnh tin tin, nh gio mu mc tiu biu nm hc 2010-2011 trn a bn H Ni, Ph Ch tch nc Nguyn Th Doan  trao tng 60 triu ng cho Cng on ngnh GD&amp;T TP. H Ni nhm h tr gio vin c hon cnh kh khn; trao tng 10 triu ng cho hc sinh Nguyn Trung Hiu (Trng THPT chuyn H Ni - Amsterdam) do  vit nn bi vn xut sc "Th gi m gy hiu ng tt cho hc sinh trong thi gian va qua.</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>Ti H Ni, L tuyn dng cc in hnh tin tin, nh gio mu mc tiu biu nm hc 2010-2011  c S GD&amp;T long trng t chc vi s tham d ca Ph Ch tch nc Nguyn Th Doan, B trng B GD&amp;T Phm V Lun... Gim c S GD-T H Ni, ng Nguyn Hu  cho bit, hng ti k nim ngy L hin chng cc nh gio hng nm, S GD&amp;T H Ni lun t ra cc mc tiu phn u i vi gio vin, gp phn xy dng mi trng gio dc thn thin, trong sch. Trong nm hc va qua, H Ni  thc hin nhiu mc tiu c th, y mnh cht lng ging dy, o to; kin ton h thng i ng gio vin; xy dng h thng trng lp t cht lng cao. H thng trng lp c m rng vi 2.400 c s gio dc, thu ht gn 1,5 triu hc sinh theo hc. Cng trong nm hc va qua, nghnh gio dc H Ni hon thnh xut sc 100% k hoch thi ua (14 ch tiu), c Th tng Chnh ph tng Bng khen n v dn u thi ua ton quc, B GD&amp;T tng C thi ua xut sc.</p>\r\n<p align="justify">Cng chung khng kh rn rng hng ti Ngy Nh gio Vit Nam, ngy 17-11, ti trng i hc  Nng  din ra L k nim Ngy Nh gio Vit Nam v tuyn dng khen thng cc c nhn, tp th xut sc c nhng ng gp cho s nghip gio dc trong nm hc 2010-2011. Nm nay, i hc  Nng c 1 tp th c Ch tch nc tng thng Hun chng c lp hng Ba; 4 c nhn c tng Hun chng Lao ng hng Ba; 1 c nhn c phong tng danh hiu chin s thi ua ton quc.</p>\r\n<p align="justify">Ti Tha Thin - Hu, ngy 17-11, S GD&amp;T  t chc L tuyn dng khen thng phong tro thi ua Hai tt; k nim tri n cc nh gio; biu dng khen thng nhng tp th, c nhn c ng gp xut sc trong ngnh gio dc. Ti bui l, Trng chuyn Quc hc Hu cng vinh d n nhn C thi ua ca Chnh ph; S GD-T Tha Thin-Hu c nhn C thi ua ca B GD-T do hon thnh xut sc 15 lnh vc, tiu ch   ra.</p>\r\n<p align="justify">Ti Tin Giang, nhiu hot ng thit thc  c t chc, nh gii bng  hc sinh-sinh vin; thi "Cm hoa, lm thip i vi gio vin; thi vit v "Ngi gio vin ca ti  c trng H An Giang t chc pht ng.</p>\r\n<p align="justify">Ti Kom Tum, mc tiu t chc ngy L hin chng cc nh gio  c S GD&amp;T  ra vi tiu ch thit thc,  ngha nhng phi tit kim, trnh lng ph. Theo lnh o S GD&amp;T Kon Tum, bng nhng n lc khng ngng, trong 20 nm qua k t khi thnh lp, ngnh gio dc tnh Kom Tum  pht trin h thng trng lp ln 363 c s gio dc, xy dng 80 trng chun quc gia. iu n tng nht l xa thnh cng 108 lng trng v gio dc; xy dng i ng gio vin vi hn 98% t chun o to. L k nim c t chc kh  ngha vi s tuyn dng 117 nh gio tiu biu thuc hai huyn ngho l Tu M Rng v Kon Plng  c nhiu n lc vt kh khn trong cng tc vn ng hc sinh ti trng.</p>\r\n<p align="right"><strong>Theo Baomoi<br /></strong></p>', 1, 30, 0, 130, '2011-11-19 14:43:02', 62, '', '2011-11-23 09:43:17', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-11-19 14:41:16', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 8, 0, 1, '', '', 0, 49, 'robots=\nauthor='),
