(58, 'Nhng im ni bt ca mt gio vin gii', 'nhng-im-ni-bt-ca-mt-giao-vien-gii', '', '<div style="font-weight: bold; padding: 10px 10px 10px 0pt; color: #4c4a4a; text-align: justify;">\r\n<table align="left" border="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://conduongmoi.com.vn/upload/news/Giao%20vien%20gioi.jpg" height="235" width="314" border="0" /></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<span style="font-size: 8pt;">Nhiu nghin cu v nhiu nh gio dc u tin rng mt yu t <span class="IL_AD" id="IL_AD4">quan trng nht  xc nh cht lng ca gio dc c th hin  cht lng ca gio vin.</span></span></div>\r\n<div style="padding: 10px 10px 10px 0pt;">\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">Vy gio vin cht lng hay gio vin gii c nhng c im g? Ngh dy hc l mt trong nhng ngh phc tp nht ngy nay. N yu cu gio vin phi c mt khi lng kin thc v mc tiu, bi ging v h tiu chun; nim am m vi ngh, thi  r rng v ngh nghip v tinh thn hc hi; phi c kin thc v nhng nguyn tc v k nng qun l lp hc; v c khao kht to ra s <span class="IL_AD" id="IL_AD6">thay i ln trong cuc sng ca tr. Vi tt c nhng yu cu  th  tr thnh mt gio vin gii qu thc rt kh.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong>* Di y l mt s c tnh ca mt gio vin gii:</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">- Gio vin gii lun t ra s k vng cao vi tt c hc sinh ca mnh: H thng k vng mi hc sinh trong lp c th v s nhn c ton b kin thc, k nng m c ging trn lp, v h khng bao gi t b mc tiu  vi nhng hc sinh cha t c kt qu tt</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">- Gio vin gii lun c nhng mc tiu r rng trong gio n: Nhng gio vin ging dy hiu qu l nhng ngi lun c k hoch bi ging  <span class="IL_AD" id="IL_AD7">cung cp <span class="IL_AD" id="IL_AD3">cho hc sinh nhng  tng r rng v iu g tr s c hc, s c giao bi tp th no v c tuyn dng khi hon thnh ra sao. Bi tp  lun c mc tiu hc tp v bi tp  lun a cho hc sinh nhiu c hi  thc hnh k nng mi. Gio vin cng lun a ra mt cch thc chm im n nh v dng bi tp c lp i lp li.</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">- Gio vin gii l ngi lun chun b tt v c tm th sn sng: H l nhng ngi lun n lp hc sm v sn sng ging dy. H trnh by bi hc mt cch r rng v c trnh t. Lp hc c t chc mt cch khoa hc v hn ch ti a nhng yu t lm t qung bi ging.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">- Gio vin gii lun bit khuyn khch hc sinh v gip hc sinh nhn nhn mt vn  trong nhiu cch khc nhau: H s dng thc t nh l mt im khi u ch khng phi l im kt thc; h lun t cu hi Ti sao, nhn vo mi kha cnh v khuyn khch hc sinh d on v iu g tip tc s xy ra. H thng xuyn t ra nhng cu hi   chc chn rng hc sinh vn ang i <span class="IL_AD" id="IL_AD5">theo mc tiu ca bi ging. H c gng pht <span class="IL_AD" id="IL_AD1">huy ton b cc thnh vin trong lp v trnh tuyt i khng  mt s hc sinh thng tr lp hc. H duy trnh s khch l hc sinh bng nhng cch tip cn trc tip v khc nhau.</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">- Gio vin gii l nhng ngi c quan h rt tt vi hc sinh v h phi cho thy hc sinh no cng c nh vy: Mt gio vin gii l ngi nhit tnh, d gn, am m v c trch nhim vi cng vic. Nhng gio vin c bit n vi nhng c im ny chnh l nhng ngi thng  li lp mun  chi vi tr v trao i thng tin vi ph huynh khi h cn. H nhit tnh tham gia cc hot ng cng ng ca nh trng v th hin s cam kt gn b vi nh trng.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">- Mt gio vin gii l ngi phi lm ch c nhng mc tiu: H th hin c s rnh mch trong mc tiu bi ging v ginh thi gian  hc thm nhng kin thc lin quan n lnh vc h ging dy. H th hin gio c trc quan ca bi ging mt cch cn thn, t m v truyn th c s ham mun hc hi nhiu hn vn  gio vin a ra.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">- Gio vin gii l ngi thng xuyn trao i thng tin vi ph huynh: H tip cn vi ph huynh thng qua cc chng trnh hi tho v thng xuyn ghi nht k gi v nh cho ph huynh. H khng ngi ngn cm in thoi gi cho ph huynh nu h thy ph huynh ang quan tm n con h.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong>* Nhng du hiu ca mt gio vin khng c nng lc:</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">- Hc sinh lun phn nn rng gio vin lun lun a ra nhng nhn xt khng tch cc v tr.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">- Gio vin lun l ngi n mun nht lp vo bui sng v ri lp u tin vo bui chiu. Khng tr li in thoi ca ph huynh hoc khng tr li th ca ph huynh.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">- Hc sinh rt t khi mang bi tp v nh.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">- Bi tp v nh thng khng c thu li hoc khng c gio vin trao i li vi hc sinh</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">- Gio vin khng gi s nht k hoc trao i thng tin vi ph huynh</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">- Gio vin th hin s hn ch v kin thc ca bi ging m mnh ging dy.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">- Bi ging thiu k hoch v khng c cu trc, trnh t r rng.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">- Gio vin t chi chp nhn bt k ng gp no ca ph huynh.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong>Thc s Nguyn Thnh on<br />Hiu trng H thng trng Mm non Hong Gia. </strong></span></p>\r\n</div>', '', 1, 24, 0, 118, '2011-11-24 07:29:16', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 62, '2011-11-29 16:49:50', '2011-11-24 07:23:48', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '', 1, 0, 1, '', '', 0, 27, ''),
(60, 'Vn lp 4: K mt cu chuyn  v mt ngi c tm lng nhn hu', 'vn-lp-4-k-mt-cau-chuyn-v-mt-ngi-co-tm-long-nhan-hu', '', '<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong>Vn lp 4: K mt cu chuyn v mt ngi c tm lng nhn hu</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong> bi:</strong> </span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">K mt cu chuyn em  c nghe hoc c c v mt ngi c tm lng nhn hu.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong>Bi lm:</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">Hin nay,  min Trung ang c l lt rt ln  cp mt ca ci v t hoa mu. <span class="IL_AD" id="IL_AD2">chia s vi nhng ngi dn min Trung, sau y , em xin k mt cu chuyn ni v iu . Cu chuyn nh sau:</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">Mt bui ti, khi hai m con ang xem ti vi th ci Hoa tht ln:</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">-M i, min Trung kh tht, m nh!</span><br /><span style="font-size: 8pt;"> -, con c bit rng by gi, min Trung ang chu ng mt thit thi rt ln khng?</span><br /><span style="font-size: 8pt;"> -Con bit ch. , m i! Ngy mai, m <span class="IL_AD" id="IL_AD1">cho con n cm rang nh, con khng n ph na u. Con dnh tin cho ngi dn min Trung c!<br />-Thi, con thch n ph th c n i, cn con thch ng h bao nhiu th m cho.\r\n<div><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><a href="http://dotchuoinon.files.wordpress.com/2011/11/07112011098.jpg"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="http://dotchuoinon.files.wordpress.com/2011/11/07112011098.jpg?w=640&h=480" width="432" border="0" height="324" /></a></span></div>\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">Nhng ci Hoa vn mt mc khng chu:</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">-Con thch t mnh ng h ch khng phi m cho tin nh th u!</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">Hnh nh cu ni   lm m n phi ng lng.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">Bng m m chm ly ci Hoa,ni:</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">-i,con gi ca m c tri tim nhn hu qu! Thi, c ri, con mun th no th m s chiu.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">Ci Hoa ti ci:</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">-Con cm n m !</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">Cu chuyn nh  trn c lm tri tim bn,suy ngh ca bn ngn rung ln khng, du l rt kh thi?</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">Khi xem ti vi, c bo, khi nhn thy cnh min Trung phi chng chi vi l, hn ai cng qun lng au xt.. Nhng sao  ch ny, ch kia vn c nhng ng tin b tiu xi phung ph. Hy mt ln lng nghe tri tim ta  chia s thm mt cht na,  ta c trong sng , p  vi tui th, ci tui th m ai cng ng c c.</span></p>\r\n<div style="text-align: right;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong>(st)</strong><br /></span></div>', '', 1, 25, 0, 119, '2011-11-24 07:33:25', 62, '', '2011-11-24 13:31:54', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-11-24 07:30:53', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '', 3, 0, 4, '', '', 0, 15, ''),
(61, 'Vit on vn ngn k v m knh yu ca em.', 'vit-on-vn-ngn-k-v-m-kinh-yeu-ca-em', '', '<p>\r\n<table align="left" border="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong><img src="http://channhu.com/VuonChanNhu/images/MeCon001.jpg" width="128" border="0" height="169" /></strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt; color: #000000;"> bi : Vit on vn ngn k v m knh yu ca em.</span></h3>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">Trong gia nh em, m l ngi m em yu qu nht. Nm nay m  ngoi ba mi tui ri nhng m cn tr lm. Dng ngi nh nhn. Khun mt tri xoan, rng r. Mi tc en mt lc no cng c chi gn gng. i mt en nhnh nhn em tht hin t v y tru mn.Thng ngy m dy tht sm  dn dpv chun b ba sng <span class="IL_AD" id="IL_AD1">cho c nh. M nu n rt ngon, em thch nht mn canh b tm ca m nu. Ti n, m thng dy em hc bi, bi no em cha hiu,m ging cho em ngay. Ri m a em vo gic ng vi nhng cu chuyn thn tin m m k, chp cnh nhng c m cho em. Em rt yu m v c gng hi c nhiu bng hoa im mi  tng m.</span><strong></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong>Bi lm ca ng Hong Anh - Lp 3A1 - Trng Tiu hc Ni o - Thy Nguyn - HP</strong></span></p>', '', 1, 25, 0, 119, '2011-11-24 07:35:55', 62, '', '2011-11-24 13:24:48', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-11-24 07:34:45', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '', 2, 0, 3, '', '', 0, 18, '');
