(62, 'Gip con kt bn khi n trng', 'giup-con-kt-bn-khi-n-trng', '', '<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">Mt trong nhng mi bn khon hng u ca cc v ph huynh c con n tui i hc l cc chu s ha nhp vi trng lp, vi bn b nh th no, c an ton khi ri b m bc vo mi trng x hi u tin y hay khng.</span></p>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><strong><span style="color: #ff6600;">Mun con i hc vi tinh thn tt nht, hy:</span></strong></span></div>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong>Dy con k nng x hi c bn<br /></strong></span><span style="font-size: 8pt;">Tr cn c hc cc k nng giao tip x hi c bn: Ni xin cho, tr li cu hi bng mt cu hon chnh ch khng phi mt t cc lc, hc cch giao tip bng nh mt v hiu tm quan trng ca vic  ngi khc ni ht cu trc khi ni xen vo.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong>Khng tr li h tr nht nht<br /></strong></span><span style="font-size: 8pt;">Nu con ca bn qu hin lnh v rt r, hy t ra thng cm, khuyn khch i vi con, song ng nhy vo tr li h con trc tt c cc cu hi. V d bn ang c mt trong siu th, c thu ngn hi con bn mt cu, hy <span class="IL_AD" id="IL_AD1">cho b c hi tr li, nh nhng khuyn khch b tr li nu b vn im lng. Tng bc mt hc ni ln suy ngh ca mnh chnh l cch gip b vt qua tnh nht nht.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong>Khuyn khch b ni v nhng g  tri qua<br /></strong></span><span style="font-size: 8pt;">Trong sut on ng t trng v nh v c thi gian sa son ba ti, hy ni chuyn vi con v nhng g con  tri qua trong ngy. Song thay v hi: Con  lm g hm nay?, bn nn k v vic bn  lm g trong ngy. Nh th con s d dng tham gia cu chuyn hn, phn ng t nhin hn. D sao ha vo cuc ni chuyn bao gi cng d hn bt u cuc ni chuyn.<br /></span></p>\r\n', '\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong>Tm bn chung ch hng</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">Tham gia vo cc hot ng ngoi kha s mang n cho con bn c hi gp g nhng tr c chung ch hng - mt cch tuyt vi  gy dng nn tnh bn. Ghi danh vo mt lp th thao cng l con ng kh nhanh  tr c thm bn b mi.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong>Chi nhm nh hay nhm ln</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">C hai u c tc dng tch cc nh nhau, hy  con ty  la chn theo  thch.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong>Cho i nh xe</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">Cch ny, bn mang n cho con c hi ha mnh vi cc bn khc, v bn thn bn cng quen bit cc ph huynh ca bn con. Thng thng cc v ph huynh s thit lp quan h vi nhau trc, t  pht trin tnh bn gia cc con ca h.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong>Lng nghe, ng can d<br /></strong></span><span style="font-size: 8pt;">i khi tr ch mun gii by, tm s cho bn bit chng ang cm thy th no v ang tri qua chuyn g m khng cn bn ng vai tr qun s. Thng thng, s tt hn c nu ph huynh khng tham gia gii quyt vic ca con, ch dng li  gip con nh nhm hn, bt lo lng hn vi nhng vn  tui hc tr.</span><br /><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong><br /></strong><strong>i vai</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">Nu pht hin ra con kh khn trong vn  kt bn, cc bc cha m c th gip con bng cch chi tr ng kch. Con s ng vai bn y nh, cn m ng vai con. Theo cch ny, bn s ch cho b thy, bng hnh ng, rng nn lm th no  lm quen vi mt bn mi, hn l ch ging gii bng li ni v bt b nghe song rt kh  thc hin.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong>Mi tr khc n nh chi<br /></strong></span><span style="font-size: 8pt;">i lc nn sp xp thi gian mi tr khc ti chi nh. Bn s trng chng bn tr, song ng can thip lc chng chi vi nhau, ri bn s thy, tr no i x tt vi con nh bn, tr no khng.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">Bn cn c th nhn ra b nh mnh c gp vn  trong giao tip x hi hay khng (qu o  hoc qu nht nht).</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">Hy coi mi cc b khc n nh l mt kinh nghim vui song cng ng qu tha thit. Nn i gia nh bn nh kia mi con bn ti chi trc khi a ra li mi tip theo.</span></p>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;">\r\n<div style="text-align: right;"><strong><span style="font-size: 8pt;">Ngun: (webtretho)</span></strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 1, 25, 0, 135, '2011-11-24 07:40:12', 62, '', '2011-12-06 06:35:18', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-11-24 07:37:20', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 4, 0, 3, '', '', 0, 7, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(63, 'Lm th no  km con bn vit ch p c?', 'lam-th-nao--kem-con-bn-vit-ch-p-c', '', '<h2 style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #008000; font-size: 10pt;"><strong>Lm th no  km con bn vit ch p c?</strong></span></h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"> tr c c nt ch p, bi vit r rng ch vit nh n hoa trn giy, b m cm quyn v ca con cm thy hi lng v ch vit con mnh th i hi ngay  tr phi c cng sc luyn rn. V ch vit c hc sinh p l nhim v rt ring bit ca thy c tiu hc .  tiu hc, nhim v l gip <span class="IL_AD" id="IL_AD4">cho cc em c thi quen vit ch <strong>CNG -THNG  TRN - U</strong> . Nhiu ph huynh gi in v email cho em hi i loi : - Con ti do ny chu xu qu, lm th no  con ti vit ch r rng, p, trong bi vit ca cc chu? Hay nh cu hi; Thy i, ti khng c iu kin cho chu hc luyn ch  nh c ? c cch no  gip cc chu vit sch p khng?</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">Ch ch Cu hi kh y Vy ti c mt s kinh nghim nh gip cc m khngc iu kin a con vo cc l luyn ch (chp m ng i hi ch vit con mnh nh ch vi tnh nh) th lm nh sau nh;Mt phng php dy ch vit p l rn luyn thc hnh nhiu .Ch c luyn nhiu mi vit p thi.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #008000; font-size: 8pt;"><strong>1. Luyn tp v luyn vit:</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">Hy mua quyn Luyn vit ch p ( gi 7 000 ng) bn nhiu  hiu sch cho chu luyn.  mi ngy ch luyn 1 bi thi. ng bt cc chu luyn nhiu n s kinh khng dm hc.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #008000; font-size: 8pt;"><strong>2. Nhc nh con quan st mu v vit <span class="IL_AD" id="IL_AD2">theo mu</span></strong><br /><span style="color: #000000;">Ai cng dy con mnh lm c iu ny: Lun nhc con hy vit v bt chc vit nh mu . Sau khi hon thnh con hy dng ch gch chn vo con ch m vit cha p Hy nh du cng vo con ch p.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #008000; font-size: 8pt;"><strong>3. Dy c