o"</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">+ Chiu cao ca ch nh ln ( v d : ch "h") v ch tht xung (v d ch "g") khng nn cao gp i ch ci nh</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">+ Ch hoa khng nn cao hn ch thng</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">+ Cc dng khi vit phi m bo ch tht xung dng trn v ch nh ln dng di khng chm vo nhau.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">+ Nhng ch kt thc  pha trn th im ni vi ch tip theo th nm ngang.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">+ Nhng ch kt thc  pha di th im ni vi ch tip theo nm cho ln</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">+ Nhng ch kt thc bng nt <span class="IL_AD" id="IL_AD3">quay v bn tri th tt nht l khng ni vo ch tip theo.</span></span></p>', 1, 25, 0, 135, '2011-11-24 07:49:15', 62, '', '2011-12-06 06:38:25', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-11-24 07:46:23', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 3, 0, 2, '', '', 0, 49, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(64, 'Phng php dy hc ton cho hc sinh trung bnh v yu  tiu hc', 'phng-phap-dy-hc-toan-cho-hc-sinh-trung-binh-va-yu-tiu-hc', '', '<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong><img style="float: right;" src="http://tbn1.google.com/images?q=tbn:RkrFTZqV92rv-M:%3Ca%20href=" />Mt trong nhng hot ng c bn ca hc sinh trong hc tp mn ton  trng&nbsp;tiu hc&nbsp;l hot ng gii ton. y l hot ng phc tp bao gm nhiu thnh t tham gia, m lu nay  c cc chuyn gia trong lnh vc phng php dy hc nghin cu v ch r.</strong> Thc tin dy hc lu nay  nc ta, <span class="IL_AD" id="IL_AD4">theo ni <span class="IL_AD" id="IL_AD2">dung, chng trnh v SGK  ban hnh, hot ng hc v gii ton ca hc sinh i tng trung bnh c bn din ra theo trnh t: quan st, tip thu kin thc; lm bi c s hng dn; t lm theo mu; c lp lm bi, tun theo qu trnh nhn thc chung l i t Algrit n ritstic.  thch ng vi qu trnh hc tp  ca a s hc sinh, kinh nghim ca gio vin dy gii cho thy, qu trnh dy cng phi c tin hnh theo 4 giai on nh sau:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br /><span style="color: #008000;"><strong><br />Giai on 1: Quan st, tip thu</strong></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">Gio vin gip hc sinh nm kin thc c bn, ti thiu, cn thit. </span><br /><span style="font-size: 8pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Gio vin cn kt hp va ging va luyn, phn tch chi tit, c th, gip hc sinh hiu khi nim khng hnh thc. </span><br /><span style="font-size: 8pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ng thi vi cung cp kin thc mi l cng c khc su thng qua v d v phn v d. Ch  phn tch cc sai lm thng gp. </span><br /><span style="font-size: 8pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Tng kt tri thc v cc tri thc phng php c trong bi. y l giai on kh khn nht, giai on lm quen tin ti hiu kin thc mi, ng thi l giai on quan trng nht, giai on cung cp kin thc chun cho hc sinh. </span><br /><span style="font-size: 8pt;">Kinh nghim cho thy khi hon thnh tt giai on ny hc sinh s tip thu tt hn  cc giai on sau.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong><span style="color: #008000;">Giai on 2: Lm theo hng dn<br /></span></strong></span><br /><span style="font-size: 8pt;">Gio vin cho v d tng t hc sinh bc u lm theo hng dn, ch o ca gio vin. Hc sinh bc u vn dng hiu bit ca mnh vo gii ton. Giai on ny thng vn cn lng tng v sai lm, do hc sinh cha thuc, cha hiu su sc. Tuy nhin giai on 2 vn c tc dng gi ng c cho giai on 3.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong><span style="color: #008000;">Giai on 3: T lm theo mu Gio vin ra mt bi tp khc, hc sinh t lm theo mu m gio vin  a ra  giai on 1 v giai on 2.</span></strong> </span><br /><span style="font-size: 8pt;">Gio vin tm ng ngoi cuc.  giai on ny hc sinh c lp thao tc. Hc sinh no hiu bi th c th hon thnh c bi tp, hc sinh no cha hiu bi s cn lng tng. Gio vin c th nm bt c vic hc tp cng nh mc  hiu bi ca c lp v tng c nhn thng qua giai on ny, t   ra bin php thch hp cho tng i tng. Giai on 3 c tc dng gi ng c trung gian. Gio vin thng vn dng giai on ny khi ra bi tp v nh.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong><span style="color: #008000;">Giai on 4: c lp lm bi tp</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">Gio vin nn ra cho hc sinh: </span><br /><span style="font-size: 8pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Hoc l mt bi tp tng t khc  hc sinh lm ngay ti lp.</span><span style="font-size: 8pt;"></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Hoc l bi tp ra v nh tng t vi bi c hc, nhm rn luyn k nng.</span><span style="font-size: 8pt;"></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Hoc l bi kim tra th.</span><span style="font-size: 8pt;"></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Hoc l  thi ca nm hc trc, nhm kch thch hc tp b mn</span><span style="font-size: 8pt;"></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Giai on ny c tc dng gi ng c kt thc mt ni dung dy hc. Gio vin thng vn dng giai on ny trong kim tra. </span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">Cch dy hc ton theo bn giai on nh trn, tuy cha thot ly cch dy hc truyn thng, nhng  phn no t ra c hiu qu thit thc i vi SGK  c bin son lu nay, ph hp vi hnh thc dy hc theo tit (45 pht), ph hp vi trnh  nhn thc ca i tng hc sinh din i tr trong hc tp mn ton.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"> c th dy hc theo bn giai on nh trn i hi gio vin phi: </span><br /><span style="font-size: 8pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Hiu su sc kin thc v cc tri thc phng php. </span><br /><span style="font-size: 8pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Trong son bi, gio vin cn chun b c bn loi bi tp cho 4 giai on, bn cnh  cn phi bit phn bc bi tp cho tng i tng hc sinh trong lp. </span><br /><span style="font-size: 8pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; V phi bit iu hnh cc i tng hc sinh trong mt lp cng hot ng bng cch giao cho mi loi i tng mt dng bi tp ph hp vi nhn thc ca h, c nh th gi hc mi sinh ng v li cun.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong>(GD&amp;T)</strong><br /></span></p>', '', 1, 28, 0, 123, '2011-11-24 07:54:58', 62, '', '2011-11-29 10:20:13', 62, 67, '2011-11-29 14:33:48', '2011-11-24 07:51:32', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 5, 0, 1, '', '', 0, 9, 'robots=\nauthor='),
